    // ── FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"footer.tagline\": \"Safety. Service. Solutions. Cuando la seguridad es cr\\xedtica y el tiempo es limitado, la respuesta es Extinval.\",\n        \"footer.services\": \"Servicios\",\n        \"footer.company\": \"Empresa\",\n        \"footer.contactTitle\": \"Contacto Global\",\n        \"footer.nosotros\": \"Sobre Nosotros\",\n        \"footer.trayectoria\": \"Trayectoria\",\n        \"footer.certs\": \"Certificaciones\",\n        \"footer.partners\": \"Partners OEM\",\n        \"footer.oem\": \"Repuestos OEM\",\n        \"footer.clientArea\": \"\\xc1rea Clientes\",\n        \"footer.faqs\": \"FAQs\",\n        \"footer.copy\": \"\\xa9 {year} Extinval Group. Todos los derechos reservados.\",\n        \"footer.legal\": \"Aviso Legal\",\n        \"footer.privacy\": \"Privacidad\",\n        \"footer.cookies\": \"Cookies\",\n        // ── PAGE HEROES ──────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"page.home\": \"Inicio\",\n        \"breadcrumb.services\": \"Servicios\",\n        \"related.title\": \"Otras Divisiones\",\n        \"related.cta\": \"Explorar →\",\n        \"sidebar.cta.label\": \"Solicitar Propuesta T\\xe9cnica\",\n        \"sidebar.badges.title\": \"Aprobaciones Aplicables\",\n        // ── ÁREA CLIENTES PAGE ────────────────────────────────────\n        \"ac.breadcrumb\": \"\\xc1rea Clientes\",\n        \"ac.cta\": \"Solicitar Acceso\",\n        // ── NOSOTROS PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"nos.overline1\": \"Trayectoria\",\n        \"nos.overline2\": \"Log\\xedstica de Precisi\\xf3n\",\n        \"nos.overline3\": \"Propuesta de Valor\",\n        \"nos.title\": \"Qui\\xe9nes Somos\",\n        \"nos.sub\": \"M\\xe1s de 40 a\\xf1os salvaguardando la vida en el mar y en tierra. Extinval Group: Safety. Service. Solutions.\",\n        \"nos.h1\": \"NUESTRA HISTORIA\",\n        \"nos.p1\": \"Extinval es sin\\xf3nimo de seguridad naval a ambos lados del Atl\\xe1ntico. Especializados en mantenimiento, inspecci\\xf3n y suministro de sistemas FFE y LSA, hemos crecido junto a nuestros clientes expandiendo nuestra operativa desde Espa\\xf1a hacia EE. UU.\",\n        \"nos.p2\": \"Nuestra estructura da respuesta experta a tres sectores vitales: la operativa cr\\xedtica de Buques Mercantes, la seguridad masiva en Pasaje y el detalle para la N\\xe1utica de Recreo. Protegemos grandes activos y vidas humanas con la misma pasi\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nos.quote\": \"M\\xe1s de 40 a\\xf1os salvaguardando la vida en el mar.\",\n        \"nos.log.title\": \"MINIMIZAMOS EL DOWNTIME EN ESCALA\",\n        \"nos.log1.t\": \"Stock Descentralizado\",\n        \"nos.log1.d\": \"Mantenemos repuestos cr\\xedticos (OEM Hatecke/Global Davit, v\\xe1lvulas, espum\\xf3genos) en nuestros almacenes de Panam\\xe1 y EE.UU. para reducir los tiempos de aduanas y env\\xedo.\",\n        \"nos.log2.t\": \"Flying Squads — Movilidad T\\xe9cnica\",\n        \"nos.log2.d\": \"Nuestros equipos est\\xe1n listos para desplazarse a cualquier puerto secundario dentro de nuestras \\xe1reas de influencia, asegurando que el barco no tenga que desviarse para recibir servicio.\",\n        \"nos.log3.t\": \"Coordinaci\\xf3n Global\",\n        \"nos.log3.d\": \"Un solo punto de contacto para gestionar inspecciones en m\\xfaltiples puertos. Planificamos el mantenimiento de su flota aprovechando las paradas naturales de la ruta comercial.\",\n        \"nos.pv.title\": \"TRES GARANT\\xcdAS,\\nUNA MISI\\xd3N GLOBAL\",\n        \"nos.pv1.t\": \"Excelencia Certificada\",\n        \"nos.pv1.d\": \"Homologaciones IACS con las cinco principales sociedades de clasificaci\\xf3n. Partners oficiales de fabricantes como ACR Electronics y Onguard. Cada certificado emitido es un documento legal blindado.\",\n        \"nos.pv2.t\": \"Log\\xedstica de Precisi\\xf3n\",\n        \"nos.pv2.d\": \"Adaptada a los tiempos de escala de su buque. Stock descentralizado en Panam\\xe1 y EE.UU. Flying Squads desplegables en cualquier puerto dentro de nuestras \\xe1reas de influencia.\",\n        \"nos.pv3.t\": \"Cumplimiento Normativo\",\n        \"nos.pv3.d\": \"Blindamos su operativa ante cualquier inspecci\\xf3n internacional: Port State Control, RightShip y Vetting de petroleras. La misma exigencia naval, ahora tambi\\xe9n en tierra.\",\n        // ── AUTORIDAD PAGE ────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"aut.pg.overline\": \"Competencia Verificada\",\n        \"aut.rep.overline\": \"Repuestos OEM\",\n        \"aut.iacs.sub\": \"Auditor\\xeda al M\\xe1ximo Nivel\",\n        \"aut.flag.sub\": \"Competencia Legal Internacional\",\n        \"aut.oem.sub\": \"Acceso Directo a Tecnolog\\xeda Original\",\n        \"aut.iso.sub\": \"Gesti\\xf3n de Calidad Certificada\",\n        \"aut.pg.title\": \"Respaldo de Autoridad\",\n        \"aut.pg.sub\": \"El pasaporte para operar globalmente. Certificaciones IACS, aprobaciones de Bandera y partners OEM.\",\n        \"aut.pg.h2\": \"EL PASAPORTE PARA OPERAR GLOBALMENTE\",\n        \"aut.pg.lead\": \"En la industria mar\\xedtima, la confianza no se pide; se demuestra con auditor\\xedas. Nuestra competencia t\\xe9cnica no es una promesa de marketing, es un hecho validado por los organismos m\\xe1s exigentes del mundo. Cada certificado que emitimos es un documento legal blindado ante cualquier PSC, RightShip o Vetting de petroleras.\",\n        \"aut.iacs.t\": \"Sociedades de Clasificaci\\xf3n (IACS)\",\n        \"aut.iacs.d\": \"Nuestros procedimientos, t\\xe9cnicos e instalaciones son auditados peri\\xf3dicamente por los miembros de la IACS. Operamos bajo los est\\xe1ndares m\\xe1s estrictos para garantizar que el seguro de Casco y M\\xe1quinas (H&M) de su buque mantenga su validez intacta.\",\n        \"aut.flag.t\": \"Aprobaciones de Bandera\",\n        \"aut.flag.d\": 'Actuamos como \"Proveedores de Servicio Aprobados\" ante las administraciones mar\\xedtimas que agrupan el mayor tonelaje de la flota mundial. Certificamos equipos en buques bajo pabellones estrat\\xe9gicos sin restricciones geogr\\xe1ficas.',\n        \"aut.oem.t\": \"Aprobaciones de Fabricantes (OEM)\",\n        \"aut.oem.d\": \"Acuerdos de Servicio T\\xe9cnico Autorizado con los fabricantes. Acceso a manuales actualizados, software de diagn\\xf3stico propietario y repuestos leg\\xedtimos. A diferencia de los talleres multimarca gen\\xe9ricos, somos el enlace directo.\",\n        \"aut.iso.d\": \"Nuestra estructura interna se rige por sistemas de gesti\\xf3n integrados que aseguran la trazabilidad de cada inspecci\\xf3n, desde la entrada del pedido hasta la emisi\\xf3n del certificado final. Excelencia estandarizada en cada servicio.\",\n        \"aut.soc.overline\": \"Certificaci\\xf3n Internacional\",\n        \"aut.soc.h2\": \"Sociedades de Clasificaci\\xf3n\",\n        \"aut.soc.lead\": \"Nuestras instalaciones, t\\xe9cnicos y procedimientos han sido auditados y aprobados por las cinco principales sociedades de clasificaci\\xf3n miembros de la IACS.\",\n        \"aut.rep.title\": \"SUMINISTRO ORIGINAL:\\nLA GARANT\\xcdA DE NO DETENCI\\xd3N\",\n        \"aut.rep.lead\": \"En el sector naval, un repuesto no conforme puede significar la inmovilizaci\\xf3n del buque. En Extinval gestionamos una divisi\\xf3n exclusiva de Repuestos Originales (OEM) con stock estrat\\xe9gico en nuestros almacenes de Espa\\xf1a y EE.UU.\",\n        \"aut.rep1.t\": \"Alianzas Estrat\\xe9gicas — Botes y Pescantes\",\n        \"aut.rep1.d\": \"Partners oficiales de Hatecke y Global Davit. Eliminamos intermediarios que encarecen y retrasan el suministro. Stock prioritario disponible en nuestros almacenes de Espa\\xf1a y EE.UU.\",\n        \"aut.rep2.t\": \"Suministros FFE y Seguridad\",\n        \"aut.rep2.d\": \"Garrafas de 20L de espumas AFFF y AR-AFFF (Baja y Alta expansi\\xf3n) con certificaci\\xf3n de lote reciente. Cargas certificadas de polvo qu\\xedmico DCP para sistemas fijos y extintores port\\xe1tiles.\",\n        \"aut.rep3.t\": \"Electr\\xf3nica y Supervivencia — ACR Electronics\",\n        \"aut.rep3.d\": \"Estaci\\xf3n autorizada para EPIRB, PLB y SART de ACR Electronics. Distribuidores de sistemas Onguard. Stock rotativo de pirotecnia para garantizar fechas de caducidad m\\xe1ximas.\",\n        // ── RED GLOBAL / RECURSOS PAGE ───────────────────────────\n        \"rg.breadcrumb\": \"Recursos\",\n        \"rg.title\": \"Recursos & Conocimiento\",\n        \"rg.sub\": \"Cobertura estrat\\xe9gica en las rutas comerciales m\\xe1s cr\\xedticas del mundo. El mismo nivel de excelencia t\\xe9cnica en cada punto del globo.\",\n        \"rg.overline\": \"Eje de Seguridad\",\n        \"rg.h2\": \"COBERTURA ESTRAT\\xc9GICA EN RUTAS CR\\xcdTICAS\",\n        \"rg.mapLabel\": \"Puntos de Operaci\\xf3n Directa\",\n        \"rg.emerg.title\": \"CONTACTO DIRECTO\",\n        \"rg.emerg.sub\": \"Equipo t\\xe9cnico especializado\",\n        \"rg.hq\": \"HQ\",\n        \"rg.loc.esp\": \"Espa\\xf1a\",\n        \"rg.loc.cnr\": \"Islas Canarias\",\n        \"rg.loc.pan\": \"Panam\\xe1\",\n        \"rg.loc.usa\": \"Norteam\\xe9rica\",\n        \"rg.pin.hq\": \"SEDE CENTRAL \\xb7 HQ\",\n        \"rg.pin.med\": \"Estrecho \\xb7 Mediterr\\xe1neo\",\n        \"rg.pin.atl\": \"Hub Atl\\xe1ntico\",\n        \"rg.pin.pan\": \"Panam\\xe1\",\n        \"rg.pin.usa\": \"Norteam\\xe9rica\",\n        \"nos.eje.lead\": \"La seguridad mar\\xedtima no entiende de fronteras, y los tiempos de escala no permiten errores log\\xedsticos. En Extinval Group hemos dise\\xf1ado nuestra expansi\\xf3n internacional siguiendo las rutas comerciales m\\xe1s exigentes del mundo en ubicaciones clave, como el Mediterr\\xe1neo y el Canal de Panam\\xe1. No somos una red de franquicias dispersa; somos un grupo consolidado con delegaciones propias en el eje Atl\\xe1ntico y Pac\\xedfico.\",\n        \"rg.blog.overline\": \"Art\\xedculos T\\xe9cnicos\",\n        \"rg.blog.h2\": \"RECURSOS & CONOCIMIENTO\",\n        \"rg.blog.lead\": \"An\\xe1lisis t\\xe9cnicos, gu\\xedas de normativa y casos pr\\xe1cticos elaborados por nuestro equipo de ingenieros especializados en seguridad mar\\xedtima e industrial.\",\n        // ── CONTACTO PAGE ────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"ct.breadcrumb\": \"Contacto\",\n        \"ct.title\": \"Contacto Global\",\n        \"ct.sub\": \"Respuesta en menos de 24h. Nuestro equipo t\\xe9cnico estar\\xe1 en contacto con usted.\",\n        \"ct.form.overline\": \"Env\\xedenos un Mensaje\",\n        \"ct.form.title\": \"SOLICITAR PROPUESTA T\\xc9CNICA\",\n        \"ct.form.name\": \"Nombre / Empresa *\",\n        \"ct.form.email\": \"Email *\",\n        \"ct.form.div\": \"Divisi\\xf3n de Inter\\xe9s *\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt1\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt2\": \"Buques Mercantes\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt3\": \"N\\xe1utica de Recreo\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt4\": \"Industrial & Comercial\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt5\": \"Repuestos OEM\",\n        \"ct.form.msg\": \"Descripci\\xf3n del buque / instalaci\\xf3n y necesidad...\",\n        \"ct.form.submit\": \"Enviar Solicitud →\",\n        \"ct.form.sending\": \"Enviando...\",\n        \"ct.form.ok\": \"✓ Solicitud recibida correctamente\",\n        \"ct.form.ok.body\": \"Nuestro equipo t\\xe9cnico le contactar\\xe1 en menos de 24 horas.\",\n        \"ct.info.title\": \"Informaci\\xf3n de Contacto\",\n        \"ct.hq\": \"Sede Central\",\n        \"ct.emerg\": \"Tel\\xe9fono\",\n        \"ct.email\": \"Email General\",\n        \"ct.emerg.title\": \"CONTACTO DIRECTO\",\n        \"ct.emerg.sub\": \"Equipo t\\xe9cnico especializado\",\n        \"ct.offices.title\": \"Nuestras Oficinas\",\n        \"ct.offices.note\": \"Principal\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"nr.badge\": \"Yates & Superyates \\xb7 Ch\\xe1rter\",\n        \"nr.breadcrumb\": \"N\\xe1utica de Recreo\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.title\": \"\\xbfNecesita asistencia para su yate?\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.text\": \"Servicio de recogida en pantal\\xe1n y visita a bordo disponible en nuestras delegaciones de Valencia, Algeciras, Las Palmas y Canarias.\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.btn\": \"Solicitar Servicio a Bordo\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.supply\": \"Suministros Destacados\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.norm\": \"Normativa Aplicable\",\n        \"nr.related.title\": \"Otras Divisiones\",\n        \"nr.sup4.title\": \"4. Soluciones Ecol\\xf3gicas de Extinci\\xf3n — Vanguardia Tecnol\\xf3gica\",\n        \"nr.sup4.item1.title\": \"Aerosoles Condensados — La Tecnolog\\xeda m\\xe1s Avanzada\",\n        \"nr.sup4.item1.text\": \"Suministro e instalaci\\xf3n de la tecnolog\\xeda de extinci\\xf3n m\\xe1s avanzada y respetuosa con el medioambiente del mercado. Estos sistemas compactos ahogan el fuego a nivel molecular sin agotar el ox\\xedgeno de la sala, sin da\\xf1ar la electr\\xf3nica sensible y sin impacto en la capa de ozono.\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA SIDEBAR SUPPLY ITEMS ──────────────────────────\n        \"nr.supply.item1.title\": \"Extintores Yacht Line\",\n        \"nr.supply.item1.text\": \"Cromado, Negro Mate, Blanco, Fibra de Carbono.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item2.title\": \"Balsas ISO 9650\",\n        \"nr.supply.item2.text\": \"Recogida en pantal\\xe1n. Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item3.title\": \"EPIRB & AIS-MOB\",\n        \"nr.supply.item3.text\": \"Servicio oficial ACR Electronics.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item4.title\": \"Aerosoles Condensados\",\n        \"nr.supply.item4.text\": \"Stat-X / FirePro. Tecnolog\\xeda ecol\\xf3gica sin tuber\\xedas.\",\n        // ── SHARED BADGE LABELS ───────────────────────────────────\n        \"badge.islas.marshall\": \"Islas Marshall\",\n        \"badge.espana.ue\": \"Espa\\xf1a/UE\",\n        \"badge.marina.mercante\": \"Marina Mercante\",\n        \"badge.iso9650\": \"ISO 9650-1 y 9650-2\",\n        // ── FAQ PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"faq.breadcrumb\": \"FAQs\",\n        \"faq.title\": \"Preguntas Frecuentes\",\n        \"faq.sub\": \"Todo lo que necesita saber sobre nuestros servicios, certificaciones y cobertura global.\",\n        \"faq.tab.all\": \"Todas\",\n        \"faq.tab.buques\": \"Buques Mercantes\",\n        \"faq.tab.oilgas\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"faq.tab.nautica\": \"N\\xe1utica de Recreo\",\n        \"faq.tab.industria\": \"Industria\",\n        // FAQ General\n        \"faq.gen.q1\": \"\\xbfD\\xf3nde se encuentran las oficinas y sedes t\\xe9cnicas de Extinval?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a1\": \"Disponemos de una red de delegaciones propias y centros de servicio para garantizar una cobertura log\\xedstica global:\\n\\nSede Central (HQ): Carrer Serra d'Espad\\xe0, 28, Aldaia (Valencia, Espa\\xf1a).\\n\\nDelegaciones en Espa\\xf1a: Las Palmas de Gran Canaria y Almer\\xeda.\\n\\nEstados Unidos: Sedes en New Jersey (Harrison), Louisiana (Saint Rose), California (Alameda) y cobertura regional desde Houston/Miami.\\n\\nAm\\xe9rica Internacional: Centros de servicio en Panam\\xe1 y Canad\\xe1.\",\n        \"faq.gen.q2\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 certificaciones avalan los servicios de inspecci\\xf3n?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a2\": \"Nuestros procesos operan bajo la certificaci\\xf3n ISO 9001:2015. Estamos auditados y aprobados por las principales sociedades de clasificaci\\xf3n miembros de la IACS: DNV, Lloyd's Register, Bureau Veritas (BV), ABS y RINA. Esto nos permite emitir certificados v\\xe1lidos para las banderas m\\xe1s exigentes (Espa\\xf1a/UE, Panam\\xe1, Liberia, Bahamas, Islas Marshall).\",\n        \"faq.gen.q3\": \"\\xbfC\\xf3mo puedo contactar con el equipo t\\xe9cnico ante una incidencia?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a3\": \"Puede contactarnos directamente por tel\\xe9fono (+34 96 367 40 53) o por email (service@extinval.com). Nuestro equipo t\\xe9cnico gestionar\\xe1 su consulta y le dar\\xe1 respuesta a la mayor brevedad posible.\",\n        // FAQ Buques Mercantes\n        \"faq.buques.q1\": \"\\xbfC\\xf3mo garantizan que el buque supere el Port State Control (PSC) sin detenciones?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a1\": 'Aplicamos un protocolo de \"blindaje t\\xe9cnico total\". Revisamos y certificamos todos los sistemas de supervivencia (LSA) y extinci\\xf3n (FFE) bajo la estricta normativa SOLAS / IMO, garantizando la operatividad de los equipos en Sala de M\\xe1quinas, Cubierta y Puente para asegurar \"Cero Deficiencias\".',\n        \"faq.buques.q2\": \"\\xbfTienen capacidad para certificar botes salvavidas y pescantes de origen asi\\xe1tico?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a2\": \"Absolutamente. Realizamos la inspecci\\xf3n anual y quinquenal (con pruebas de carga estructural o Load Testing) estando certificados por fabricantes l\\xedderes europeos (Hatecke, Global Davit) y los principales Key Players asi\\xe1ticos (Jiangsu Jiaoyan, Shigi, Mansei, Oriental, Hyundai/Bada y Qingdao Beihai).\",\n        \"faq.buques.q3\": \"\\xbfEs posible realizar la calibraci\\xf3n de todos los equipos en una sola visita a bordo?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a3\": \"S\\xed. Optimizamos el tiempo de escala certificando en una sola intervenci\\xf3n los detectores de gas, alcohol\\xedmetros, man\\xf3metros y medidores UTI (Interfase/Temperatura), ofreciendo trazabilidad total para el PSC y el vetting de petroleras.\",\n        \"faq.buques.q4\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 ocurre si el barco escala en un puerto secundario donde no hay sede de Extinval?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a4\": \"Desplegamos a nuestros Flying Squads, equipos t\\xe9cnicos de respuesta r\\xe1pida que se desplazan al puerto de escala. El barco no tiene que desviarse de su ruta comercial, minimizando el downtime. Adem\\xe1s, contamos con stock descentralizado de repuestos OEM en Panam\\xe1 y EE. UU. para env\\xedos r\\xe1pidos.\",\n        // FAQ Oil & Gas\n        \"faq.oilgas.q1\": \"\\xbfEst\\xe1n capacitados para intervenir en atm\\xf3sferas explosivas (ATEX)?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a1\": \"S\\xed. Nuestros especialistas gestionan y calibran redes de sensores fijos (LEL, H2S, CO, O2) y detectores \\xf3pticos de llama (IR/UV) en entornos ATEX. Adem\\xe1s, suministramos flotas de detectores multigas y comunicaciones de emergencia (Radios UHF/VHF, PLB) intr\\xednsecamente seguras.\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q2\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 mantenimiento espec\\xedfico requieren los sistemas de extinci\\xf3n en plataformas?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a2\": \"Realizamos el mantenimiento integral de bancos masivos de CO2, sistemas de gases limpios (Novec 1230 / Inergen) y pruebas de fluidificaci\\xf3n y soplado de l\\xedneas en grandes estaciones fijas de polvo (Skids) dise\\xf1adas para combatir fuegos de gas a presi\\xf3n (Jet Fires).\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q3\": \"\\xbfEs obligatorio analizar los espum\\xf3genos de los sistemas de diluvio?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a3\": \"S\\xed, es un requisito normativo. Realizamos el an\\xe1lisis qu\\xedmico de laboratorio para espum\\xf3genos (AR-AFFF) sometidos a condiciones extremas marinas. Adem\\xe1s, tenemos capacidad de suministro inmediato de nuevas f\\xf3rmulas sin fl\\xfaor (SFFF) en formato IBC de 1.000L.\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q4\": \"\\xbfC\\xf3mo protegen al personal ante la fuga de gases letales como el H2S?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a4\": \"Suministramos capuces de escape r\\xe1pido (EEBD) y realizamos el mantenimiento de sistemas de cascada de aire respirable (Air Cascade Systems). Certificamos los compresores de alta presi\\xf3n bajo la norma EN 12021 para garantizar un aire 100% seguro en espacios confinados.\",\n        // FAQ Náutica de Recreo\n        \"faq.nautica.q1\": '\\xbfQu\\xe9 significa el enfoque \"Guante Blanco\" en sus inspecciones a bordo?',\n        \"faq.nautica.a1\": \"Sabemos que la est\\xe9tica es fundamental en un superyate. Nuestro personal protege cuidadosamente las cubiertas de teca y los interiores premium durante la revisi\\xf3n de extintores y sistemas fijos (FFE), garantizando una intervenci\\xf3n limpia y sin impacto visual.\",\n        \"faq.nautica.q2\": \"\\xbfExisten extintores que cumplan la normativa sin alterar el dise\\xf1o del yate?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a2\": 'S\\xed, disponemos de la colecci\\xf3n \"Yacht Line\". Son extintores de alta eficacia con acabados premium (Cromado, Negro Mate, Blanco y Fibra de Carbono) dise\\xf1ados para integrarse perfectamente en la est\\xe9tica de los salones y camarotes de lujo.',\n        \"faq.nautica.q3\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 sistemas fijos recomiendan para proteger la sala de m\\xe1quinas sin da\\xf1ar los motores?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a3\": \"Recomendamos e instalamos agentes limpios (Novec 1230, FM-200 o HFC-227ea) o generadores de aerosol ultracompactos (Stat-X / FirePro). Estos sistemas extinguen el fuego sin dejar residuos perjudiciales para la electr\\xf3nica o la mec\\xe1nica de alto valor.\",\n        \"faq.nautica.q4\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 equipos gestionan relacionados con el salvamento (LSA) y la electr\\xf3nica de seguridad?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a4\": \"Realizamos la revisi\\xf3n de balsas ISO 9650 (marcas como Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf) con servicio de recogida en pantal\\xe1n. Adem\\xe1s, como servicio oficial de ACR Electronics, certificamos radiobalizas (EPIRB, PLB) y transpondedores AIS (Clase A y B). Tambi\\xe9n nos encargamos de la destrucci\\xf3n certificada de pirotecnia caducada.\",\n        // FAQ Industrial\n        \"faq.industrial.q1\": \"\\xbfQu\\xe9 aporta una empresa del sector mar\\xedtimo a una instalaci\\xf3n industrial terrestre?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a1\": \"Trasladamos la disciplina extrema, certificaciones y trazabilidad documental exigida por las normativas mar\\xedtimas (IACS) a las plantas qu\\xedmicas, naves log\\xedsticas o centros de datos. Esto asegura que los sistemas de rociadores, polvo o espumas ofrezcan la m\\xe1xima fiabilidad en tierra.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q2\": \"\\xbfC\\xf3mo evitan las falsas alarmas que provocan paradas de producci\\xf3n?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a2\": \"Realizamos Auditor\\xedas de Sensibilidad en sistemas centralizados de detecci\\xf3n (Siemens, Honeywell, Hochiki, Apollo, Notifier) para asegurar una respuesta temprana ante incendios reales sin sufrir falsas alarmas provocadas por el polvo, la humedad o las altas temperaturas industriales.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q3\": \"\\xbfEs posible actualizar el sistema de incendios de mi local o nave sin realizar obra civil?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a3\": \"S\\xed. Instalamos sistemas de detecci\\xf3n inal\\xe1mbrica (Wireless) que no requieren cables ni rozas en paredes, reduciendo el tiempo de instalaci\\xf3n a la mitad. Asimismo, implementamos Aerosoles Condensados, una tecnolog\\xeda de extinci\\xf3n molecular sin impacto ecol\\xf3gico que se instala en un solo d\\xeda sin tuber\\xedas.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q4\": \"\\xbfTienen validez legal las calibraciones de detectores de gas realizadas en industria?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a4\": \"Totalmente. Emitimos certificados de calibraci\\xf3n para espacios confinados con patrones trazables a organismos nacionales e internacionales (ENAC / PTB / NIST), garantizando que su empresa supere cualquier inspecci\\xf3n de Industria o de Riesgos Laborales.\",\n        // ── HERO SLIDES ──────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"slide1.division\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"slide1.claim1\": \"M\\xc1XIMA FIABILIDAD\",\n        \"slide1.claim2\": \"EN ENTORNOS DE RIESGO CR\\xcdTICO\",\n        \"slide1.lead\": \"Plataformas offshore, Drillships y refiner\\xedas. Sistemas FFE de alta capacidad, calibraci\\xf3n ATEX e inspecci\\xf3n LSA bajo est\\xe1ndares IACS.\",\n        \"slide2.division\": \"Buques Mercantes\",\n        \"slide2.claim1\": \"CERO\",\n        \"slide2.claim2\": \"DEFICIENCIAS.\",\n        \"slide2.claim3\": \"CERO RETRASOS.\",\n        \"slide2.lead\": \"Blindaje t\\xe9cnico total ante el Port State Control. Log\\xedstica de precisi\\xf3n adaptada a los tiempos de escala de su buque.\",\n        \"slide3.division\": \"N\\xe1utica de Recreo\",\n        \"slide3.claim1\": \"NAVEGAR\",\n        \"slide3.claim2\": \"TRANQUILO,\",\n        \"slide3.claim3\": \"PUNTO.\",\n        \"slide3.subtitle\": \"Est\\xe9tica y funcionalidad\",\n        \"slide3.lead\": 'Servicio \"Guante Blanco\" para Yates, Superyates y Ch\\xe1rter. M\\xe1xima discreci\\xf3n, m\\xednimo impacto visual.',\n        \"slide4.division\": \"Industrial & Comercial\",\n        \"slide4.claim1\": \"RIGOR NAVAL\",\n        \"slide4.claim2\": \"APLICADO A LA\",\n        \"slide4.claim3\": \"INDUSTRIA TERRESTRE.\",\n        \"slide4.lead\": \"Trasladamos la exigencia extrema del sector mar\\xedtimo a sus instalaciones. Aerosoles condensados, detecci\\xf3n inal\\xe1mbrica, trazabilidad total.\",\n        // ── PORTFOLIO ITEMS ───────────────────────────────────────\n        \"pt1.cat\": \"FFE — Extinci\\xf3n\",\n        \"pt1.name\": \"Sistemas Fijos CO₂, Espuma & Niebla\",\n        \"pt1.desc\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n anual y quinquenal IACS. An\\xe1lisis laboratorio AR-AFFF.\",\n        \"pt2.cat\": \"LSA — Salvamento\",\n        \"pt2.name\": \"Botes & Pescantes Ca\\xedda Libre\",\n        \"pt2.desc\": \"Hatecke, Global Davit, Jiangsu Jiaoyan. Load Testing certificado.\",\n        \"pt3.cat\": \"ATEX — Detecci\\xf3n\",\n        \"pt3.name\": \"Calibraci\\xf3n Gases H₂S / LEL\",\n        \"pt3.desc\": \"Certificados trazables para PSC y vetting de petroleras.\",\n        \"pt4.cat\": \"N\\xe1utica\",\n        \"pt4.name\": \"Balsas ISO & Pirotecnia\",\n        \"pt4.desc\": \"ISO 9650. Gesti\\xf3n certificada de pirotecnia caducada.\",\n        \"pt5.cat\": \"GMDSS / Radio\",\n        \"pt5.name\": \"EPIRB \\xb7 AIS \\xb7 SART\",\n        \"pt5.desc\": \"Servicio oficial ACR Electronics. Programaci\\xf3n MMSI.\",\n        \"pt6.cat\": \"Industrial\",\n        \"pt6.name\": \"Aerosoles & Detecci\\xf3n Wireless\",\n        \"pt6.desc\": \"Extinci\\xf3n molecular. Sin obra civil. Tecnolog\\xeda ecol\\xf3gica.\",\n        \"pt7.cat\": \"OEM Repuestos\",\n        \"pt7.name\": \"Stock Estrat\\xe9gico ESP/USA\",\n        \"pt7.desc\": \"Distribuci\\xf3n oficial Hatecke, Global Davit, Viking, Zodiac.\",\n        // ── ISO STRIP ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"iso.sub\": \"Gesti\\xf3n de Calidad Certificada\",\n        // ── RELATED CARD DESCRIPTIONS ─────────────────────────────\n        \"related.og.d\": \"M\\xe1xima fiabilidad en entornos offshore y de riesgo cr\\xedtico.\",\n        \"related.bm.d\": \"Cero deficiencias ante el Port State Control. SOLAS / IMO.\",\n        \"related.nr.d\": 'Servicio \"Guante Blanco\" para Yates y Superyates.',\n        \"related.ic.d\": \"Rigor naval aplicado a instalaciones industriales en tierra.\",\n        // ── OIL & GAS PAGE CHROME ─────────────────────────────────\n        \"og.badge\": \"Sector Cr\\xedtico — Offshore & Refiner\\xedas\",\n        \"og.sidebar.title\": \"\\xbfNecesita asistencia t\\xe9cnica?\",\n        \"og.sidebar.text\": \"Nuestros especialistas O&G est\\xe1n listos para atender cualquier incidencia en plataforma, Drillship o refiner\\xeda.\",\n        \"og.sidebar.btn\": \"Contactar\",\n        \"og.sidebar.supply\": \"Capacidad de Suministro OEM\",\n        \"og.sup1.title\": \"Espum\\xf3genos AR-AFFF\",\n        \"og.sup1.text\": \"IBCs 1.000L. Sin fl\\xfaor (SFFF) disponible.\",\n        \"og.sup2.title\": \"Multigas ATEX/IECEx\",\n        \"og.sup2.text\": \"4–6 gases. Detectores para operarios.\",\n        \"og.sup3.title\": \"Radios ATEX\",\n        \"og.sup3.text\": \"UHF/VHF intr\\xednsecamente seguras. PLBs.\",\n        \"og.sup4.title\": \"EPIs Offshore\",\n        \"og.sup4.text\": \"SCBA, EEBDs, Trajes SOLAS, Ground Monitors.\",\n        // ── BUQUES MERCANTES PAGE CHROME ──────────────────────────\n        \"bm.badge\": \"SOLAS / IMO — Cumplimiento Normativo\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.title\": \"\\xbfBuque en puerto?\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.text\": \"Minimizamos el downtime. Nuestros Flying Squads se desplazan al buque en escala. Un solo punto de contacto para gestionar todas las inspecciones.\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.btn\": \"Contactar\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.logistics\": \"Log\\xedstica de Precisi\\xf3n\",\n        \"bm.log1.title\": \"Stock Descentralizado\",\n        \"bm.log1.text\": \"Repuestos OEM en Panam\\xe1 y EE.UU. — m\\xednimos tiempos de aduana y env\\xedo.\",\n        \"bm.log2.title\": \"Flying Squads\",\n        \"bm.log2.text\": \"Equipos t\\xe9cnicos a cualquier puerto secundario. El barco no tiene que desviarse.\",\n        \"bm.log3.title\": \"Coordinaci\\xf3n Global\",\n        \"bm.log3.text\": \"Un solo punto de contacto para toda la flota y m\\xfaltiples puertos.\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.approvals\": \"Aprobaciones\",\n        // ── INDUSTRIAL & COMERCIAL PAGE CHROME ────────────────────\n        \"ic.badge\": \"Rigor Naval en Tierra Firme\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.title\": \"\\xbfNecesita un diagn\\xf3stico?\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.text\": \"Le realizamos una auditor\\xeda gratuita de su instalaci\\xf3n actual y le presentamos un plan de mantenimiento adaptado a sus necesidades y presupuesto.\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.btn\": \"Solicitar Auditor\\xeda\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.tech\": \"Tecnolog\\xedas Destacadas\",\n        \"ic.tech1.title\": \"Aerosoles Condensados\",\n        \"ic.tech1.text\": \"Extinci\\xf3n molecular. Sin da\\xf1o electr\\xf3nico. Sin obra civil.\",\n        \"ic.tech2.title\": \"Detecci\\xf3n Wireless\",\n        \"ic.tech2.text\": \"Sin cables, sin obras. Instalaci\\xf3n en un d\\xeda.\",\n        \"ic.tech3.title\": \"Calibraci\\xf3n ATEX\",\n        \"ic.tech3.text\": \"Certificados trazables ENAC/PTB/NIST.\",\n        \"ic.tech4.title\": \"Extintores\",\n        \"ic.tech4.text\": \"Polvo, CO₂, H\\xeddricos, Espuma. Adaptados por zona.\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.adv\": \"Ventaja Competitiva\",\n        \"ic.adv1.label\": \"LR \\xb7 RINA \\xb7 DNV \\xb7 ABS \\xb7 BV\",\n        \"ic.adv1.text\": \"Las mismas certificaciones mar\\xedtimas aplicadas a tierra\",\n        \"ic.adv2.label\": \"ISO 9001:2015\",\n        \"ic.adv2.text\": \"Trazabilidad total de cada intervenci\\xf3n\",\n        \"ic.adv3.label\": \"Respuesta T\\xe9cnica\",\n        \"ic.adv3.text\": \"Para instalaciones cr\\xedticas con contrato de mantenimiento\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.sectors\": \"Sectores que Atendemos\",\n        \"ic.sector1\": \"Naves Industriales\",\n        \"ic.sector2\": \"Centros Log\\xedsticos\",\n        \"ic.sector3\": \"Edificios Comerciales\",\n        \"ic.sector4\": \"Plantas Qu\\xedmicas\",\n        \"ic.sector5\": \"Centros de Datos\",\n        \"ic.sector6\": \"Hospitales\",\n        \"ic.sector7\": \"Edificios Hist\\xf3ricos\",\n        \"ic.sector8\": \"Sector Retail\",\n        // ── OIL & GAS PAGE CONTENT ────────────────────────────────\n        \"og.subtitle\": \"M\\xe1xima Fiabilidad en Entornos de Riesgo Cr\\xedtico. Plataformas offshore, Drillships y refiner\\xedas.\",\n        \"og.intro\": \"El sector del Oil & Gas opera bajo los est\\xe1ndares de seguridad m\\xe1s implacables del mundo. Un fallo t\\xe9cnico en una plataforma offshore, un buque perforador (Drillship) o una refiner\\xeda no es una opci\\xf3n. En Extinval aportamos nuestra m\\xe1xima capacidad de ingenier\\xeda para garantizar la protecci\\xf3n de activos de alto valor y, sobre todo, la vida del personal en atm\\xf3sferas explosivas y entornos hostiles.\",\n        \"og.srv.title\": \"Servicios de Inspecci\\xf3n y Mantenimiento (FFE & LSA)\",\n        \"og.s1.title\": \"1. Sistemas Fijos de Extinci\\xf3n de Alta Capacidad (FFE)\",\n        \"og.s1.i1.t\": \"Sistemas de Espuma, Diluvio y Polvo\",\n        \"og.s1.i1.d\": \"Mantenimiento en \\xe1reas de proceso. An\\xe1lisis qu\\xedmico obligatorio de laboratorio para espum\\xf3genos (AR-AFFF) sometidos a condiciones marinas extremas. Revisi\\xf3n de grandes estaciones fijas de polvo (Skids) vitales para la extinci\\xf3n de fuegos de gas a presi\\xf3n (Jet Fires). Pruebas de fluidificaci\\xf3n y soplado de l\\xedneas.\",\n        \"og.s1.i2.t\": \"Bancos CO₂ y Gases Limpios (Novec 1230 / Inergen)\",\n        \"og.s1.i2.d\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n de bancos masivos de CO₂ para salas de turbinas y generadores. Sistemas de gases limpios Novec 1230 e Inergen para la protecci\\xf3n de las salas de control (CCR) y armarios el\\xe9ctricos cr\\xedticos.\",\n        \"og.s2.title\": \"2. Detecci\\xf3n de Gases y Atm\\xf3sferas Peligrosas (ATEX)\",\n        \"og.s2.i1.t\": \"Redes de Sensores Fijos en Planta — LEL, H₂S, CO, O₂\",\n        \"og.s2.i1.d\": \"Mantenimiento y calibraci\\xf3n con gas patr\\xf3n de redes de sensores fijos: Gases Combustibles (LEL), Sulfuro de Hidr\\xf3geno (H₂S, el riesgo m\\xe1s mortal en O&G), Mon\\xf3xido de Carbono (CO) y deficiencia de Ox\\xedgeno. Trazabilidad total de certificados.\",\n        \"og.s2.i2.t\": \"Detectores \\xd3pticos de Llama IR/UV/CCTV\",\n        \"og.s2.i2.d\": \"Pruebas funcionales de detectores \\xf3pticos dise\\xf1ados para no emitir falsas alarmas con la luz solar o los reflejos del mar. Calibraci\\xf3n con fuentes de referencia certificadas.\",\n        \"og.s3.title\": \"3. Evacuaci\\xf3n y Supervivencia Offshore (LSA)\",\n        \"og.s3.i1.t\": \"Botes Salvavidas de Ca\\xedda Libre (Free-fall Lifeboats)\",\n        \"og.s3.i1.d\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n anual y quinquenal de sistemas de liberaci\\xf3n hidr\\xe1ulica y estructural de botes de evacuaci\\xf3n r\\xe1pida. Sistemas de Transferencia de Personal: revisi\\xf3n de redes, cestas de transferencia (Frog/Billy Pugh) y balsas salvavidas de pescante.\",\n        \"og.s3.i2.t\": \"Trajes de Supervivencia e Inspecci\\xf3n de Sistemas SCBA\",\n        \"og.s3.i2.d\": \"Pruebas de estanqueidad y presi\\xf3n para trajes de inmersi\\xf3n y supervivencia adaptados a la industria del petr\\xf3leo. Mantenimiento de unidades de suministro de aire (Air Cascade Systems) para trabajos en espacios confinados.\",\n        \"og.s4.title\": \"4. Soporte Vital y Calidad de Aire\",\n        \"og.s4.i1.t\": \"Sistemas de Cascada y Aire Respirable\",\n        \"og.s4.i1.d\": \"Mantenimiento de unidades m\\xf3viles y fijas de suministro de aire (Air Cascade Systems) para trabajos en espacios confinados. Certificaci\\xf3n de compresores de alta presi\\xf3n seg\\xfan EN 12021 / CGA G-7.1 para garantizar que el aire de los equipos SCBA y capuces de escape es 100% seguro.\",\n        \"og.sup.title\": \"Suministros — Tecnolog\\xeda, Repuestos OEM y Seguridad ATEX\",\n        \"og.sup1.h\": \"1. Agentes Extintores de Alto Rendimiento\",\n        \"og.sup1.i1.t\": \"Espum\\xf3genos Especiales (SFFF y AR-AFFF)\",\n        \"og.sup1.i1.d\": \"Suministro de concentrados de espuma sin fl\\xfaor (SFFF) y resistentes al alcohol (AR-AFFF) en grandes vol\\xfamenes — bidones e IBCs de 1.000L — para reposici\\xf3n inmediata tras una emergencia o prueba.\",\n        \"og.sup1.i2.t\": \"Polvo Qu\\xedmico Seco de Grado Superior\",\n        \"og.sup1.i2.d\": \"Polvo qu\\xedmico seco (DCP) tratado con silicona para evitar la compactaci\\xf3n por las vibraciones de la plataforma. Cargas certificadas para sistemas fijos y extintores port\\xe1tiles.\",\n        \"og.sup2.h\": \"2. Equipamiento ATEX y Detecci\\xf3n Port\\xe1til\",\n        \"og.sup2.i1.t\": \"Detectores Multigas Port\\xe1tiles (ATEX / IECEx)\",\n        \"og.sup2.i1.d\": \"Venta y suministro de flotas de detectores personales de 4 a 6 gases para operarios, con certificaciones intr\\xednsecamente seguras ATEX/IECEx. Gesti\\xf3n de contratos de calibraci\\xf3n peri\\xf3dica incluida.\",\n        \"og.sup2.i2.t\": \"Comunicaciones de Emergencia — Radios ATEX y PLBs\",\n        \"og.sup2.i2.d\": \"Suministro de radios UHF/VHF intr\\xednsecamente seguras y radiobalizas personales (PLB) para el personal de cubierta en zonas con atm\\xf3sfera explosiva potencial.\",\n        \"og.sup3.h\": \"3. Protecci\\xf3n Respiratoria y Lucha Contra Incendios\",\n        \"og.sup3.i1.t\": \"Equipos de Escape H₂S (EEBD) y Equipamiento Pesado\",\n        \"og.sup3.i1.d\": \"Capuces de escape r\\xe1pido espec\\xedficos para emergencias por fugas de gas t\\xf3xico. Extintores m\\xf3viles de ruedas (hasta 135L o 50kg) con recubrimientos marinos para resistir la corrosi\\xf3n salina extrema.\",\n        \"og.sup3.i2.t\": \"Ca\\xf1ones de Agua/Espuma de Alto Caudal (Ground Monitors)\",\n        \"og.sup3.i2.d\": \"Monitores port\\xe1tiles de alto caudal para despliegue r\\xe1pido en \\xe1reas de proceso. Estrategia defensiva de primer nivel ante incendios de gran magnitud en plataforma.\",\n        // ── BUQUES MERCANTES PAGE CONTENT ─────────────────────────\n        \"bm.title\": \"Buques Mercantes\",\n        \"bm.subtitle\": \"Cero Deficiencias. Cero Retrasos. Blindaje t\\xe9cnico total ante el Port State Control para buques de carga, tanqueros, graneleros y portacontenedores.\",\n        \"bm.intro\": \"Nuestra divisi\\xf3n mercante est\\xe1 dise\\xf1ada para blindar t\\xe9cnicamente a buques de carga, tanqueros, graneleros y portacontenedores. Entendemos la presi\\xf3n del Port State Control; por ello, nuestros protocolos aseguran la operatividad total de los sistemas cr\\xedticos en Sala de M\\xe1quinas, Cubierta y Puente.\",\n        \"bm.srv.title\": \"Servicios de Inspecci\\xf3n y Mantenimiento (FFE & LSA)\",\n        \"bm.s1.title\": \"1. Sistemas Fijos de Extinci\\xf3n\",\n        \"bm.s1.i1.t\": \"CO₂ (+200 cilindros), Water Mist y Espuma\",\n        \"bm.s1.i1.d\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n anual y quinquenal de sistemas CO₂ (escalable a m\\xe1s de 200 cilindros), Water Mist (Niebla de Agua) y Espuma de Baja y Alta expansi\\xf3n. An\\xe1lisis de laboratorio obligatorio para espum\\xf3genos sometidos a condiciones marinas extremas.\",\n        \"bm.s1.i2.t\": \"Niebla de Agua para Sala de M\\xe1quinas y Cocina\",\n        \"bm.s1.i2.d\": \"Revisi\\xf3n de sistemas de niebla de agua para la protecci\\xf3n de sala de m\\xe1quinas, freidoras (deep fat fryers) y espacios de carga de alto riesgo. Comprobaci\\xf3n de presiones de activaci\\xf3n y boquillas.\",\n        \"bm.s2.title\": \"2. Botes y Pescantes (Lifeboats & Davits) — Load Testing\",\n        \"bm.s2.i1.t\": \"Fabricantes L\\xedderes Certificados — Europa y Asia\",\n        \"bm.s2.i1.d\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n anual y quinquenal con aprobaciones IACS y de Bandera/Clase. Europa: Hatecke, Global Davit. Asian Key Players: Jiangsu Jiaoyan, Shigi, Mansei, Oriental, Hyundai Lifeboats (Bada), Qingdao Beihai.\",\n        \"bm.s2.i2.t\": \"Pruebas de Carga Estructural — Gr\\xfaas, Pescantes y Pasarelas\",\n        \"bm.s2.i2.d\": \"Certificaci\\xf3n estructural de gr\\xfaas de provisiones y pescantes. Inspecci\\xf3n cr\\xedtica de pasarelas y escaleras de acomodaci\\xf3n. Documentaci\\xf3n completa para PSC y IACS.\",\n        \"bm.s3.title\": \"3. Calibraci\\xf3n e Instrumentaci\\xf3n en una Sola Visita\",\n        \"bm.s3.i1.t\": \"Detectores de Gas, Alcohol\\xedmetros, Man\\xf3metros y UTI\",\n        \"bm.s3.i1.d\": \"Servicio integral en una sola visita a bordo: detectores de gas, alcohol\\xedmetros, man\\xf3metros y medidores UTI (Interfase/Temperatura). Certificados con trazabilidad total para PSC y vetting de petroleras.\",\n        \"bm.s3.i2.t\": \"Aire Respirable — EEBD, SCBA y Compresores\",\n        \"bm.s3.i2.d\": \"Calidad de aire de compresores seg\\xfan EN 12021. Inspecci\\xf3n de EEBD (Emergency Escape Breathing Devices) para evacuaci\\xf3n r\\xe1pida. Revisi\\xf3n de equipos SCBA para la brigada de incendios de a bordo.\",\n        \"bm.sup.title\": \"Suministros — Venta, Repuestos OEM y Avituallamiento\",\n        \"bm.sup1.title\": \"1. Repuestos Originales (OEM Parts)\",\n        \"bm.sup1.i1.t\": \"Componentes LSA para Hatecke y Global Davit\",\n        \"bm.sup1.i1.d\": \"Distribuci\\xf3n oficial de repuestos: cables de acero, ganchos de suelta hidrost\\xe1tica, piezas de motor de pescante. Trazabilidad absoluta desde el fabricante hasta la cubierta del barco. Sin intermediarios que encarezcan y retrasen el suministro.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.title\": \"2. Equipamiento de Extinci\\xf3n (FFE)\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i1.t\": \"Extintores de Gran Capacidad — Polvo y Espuma\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i1.d\": \"Carros m\\xf3viles de Polvo (50kg) y Espuma (45L / 135L) para cubierta y sala de m\\xe1quinas. Recubrimientos resistentes a la corrosi\\xf3n marina para m\\xe1xima durabilidad en entornos salinos.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i2.t\": \"Mangueras, Lanzas y Acoples Internacionales\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i2.d\": \"Mangueras de alta presi\\xf3n, lanzas de doble efecto y acoples internacionales (Storz, Nakajima, Barcelona). Hachas de bombero y herramientas de apertura forcible certificadas SOLAS.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i3.t\": \"Agentes Extintores — Espum\\xf3genos Certificados y Polvo\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i3.d\": \"Bidones de espum\\xf3geno certificado (AFFF y AR-AFFF) de \\xfaltima caducidad. Cargas de polvo qu\\xedmico DCP para sistemas fijos y extintores port\\xe1tiles. Disponible en entregas directas a bordo en nuestros puertos de operaci\\xf3n.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.title\": \"3. Seguridad Personal y Protecci\\xf3n\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i1.t\": \"Trajes T\\xe9cnicos — Bombero, Qu\\xedmico e Inmersi\\xf3n\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i1.d\": \"Trajes de bombero (SOLAS), trajes de protecci\\xf3n qu\\xedmica y trajes de inmersi\\xf3n certificados. Material de dotaci\\xf3n y repuesto para la brigada de incendios de a bordo.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i2.t\": \"Equipos SCBA Nuevos, Botellas y EEBDs\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i2.d\": \"Venta de equipos SCBA completos de nueva generaci\\xf3n. Botellas de recambio (6L y 9L). Unidades EEBD de escape r\\xe1pido para puntos de evacuaci\\xf3n en sala de m\\xe1quinas y espacios confinados.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i3.t\": \"Detectores Port\\xe1tiles — Explos\\xedmetros y Multigas\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i3.d\": \"Suministro de explos\\xedmetros y detectores multigas de \\xfaltima generaci\\xf3n para personal de cubierta y operaciones en espacios confinados. Contrato de calibraci\\xf3n peri\\xf3dica disponible.\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA DE RECREO PAGE CONTENT ────────────────────────\n        \"nr.page.subtitle\": 'Un servicio \"Guante Blanco\" para Yates, Superyates y Ch\\xe1rter. Nos encargamos de la complejidad normativa para que el armador solo se preocupe de disfrutar del mar.',\n        \"nr.intro\": 'En Extinval entendemos que un yate o superyate es la combinaci\\xf3n perfecta entre el placer de navegar y la m\\xe1s estricta responsabilidad de seguridad. A diferencia de los servicios de mantenimiento convencionales, nuestro enfoque \"Guante Blanco\" protege la est\\xe9tica de su embarcaci\\xf3n durante cada intervenci\\xf3n, garantizando que las revisiones normativas no dejen huella en sus espacios interiores o cubierta de teca. M\\xe1xima seguridad, m\\xednimo impacto visual.',\n        \"nr.srv.title\": \"Servicios de Mantenimiento, Inspecci\\xf3n y Certificaci\\xf3n\",\n        \"nr.srv1.title\": '1. Protecci\\xf3n Contra Incendios \"Clean & Safe\" (FFE)',\n        \"nr.srv1.item1.title\": \"Sistemas de Agentes Limpios\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item1.text\": \"Mantenimiento y recarga de sistemas de extinci\\xf3n autom\\xe1tica en salas de m\\xe1quinas con gases Novec 1230, FM-200 o HFC-227ea. Estos agentes extinguen el fuego sin dejar residuos, protegiendo la electr\\xf3nica y los motores de alto valor del yate.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item2.title\": \"Generadores de Aerosol (Stat-X / FirePro)\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item2.text\": \"Revisi\\xf3n de sistemas compactos de extinci\\xf3n que se activan t\\xe9rmica o el\\xe9ctricamente, ideales para espacios reducidos en veleros y motoras. Sin necesidad de tuber\\xedas ni agentes a presi\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item3.title\": 'Extintores Port\\xe1tiles — Inspecci\\xf3n \"White Glove\"',\n        \"nr.srv1.item3.text\": \"Inspecci\\xf3n cuidadosa de extintores de polvo, espuma y CO₂. Protegemos las cubiertas de teca y los interiores premium durante toda la revisi\\xf3n. Acabados cromados, negro mate y fibra de carbono disponibles.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item4.title\": \"Sistemas de Parada y Fire Dampers\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item4.text\": \"Comprobaci\\xf3n del cierre autom\\xe1tico de v\\xe1lvulas de combustible y ventiladores (Fire Dampers) al activarse la extinci\\xf3n, conforme a los requisitos de la zona de navegaci\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.title\": \"2. Detecci\\xf3n de Gases y Seguridad Ambiental\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item1.title\": \"Gases Pesados GLP / Butano en Sentinas\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item1.text\": \"Instalaci\\xf3n y calibraci\\xf3n de sensores en sentinas (donde se acumula el gas pesado) para prevenir explosiones en cocinas y zonas de generadores.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item2.title\": \"Mon\\xf3xido de Carbono (CO) en Camarotes\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item2.text\": \"Revisi\\xf3n de detectores de CO en camarotes, vital para evitar intoxicaciones silenciosas por mala combusti\\xf3n de generadores o motores auxiliares.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item3.title\": \"Alarmas de Sentina y Sensores de Nivel\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item3.text\": \"Verificaci\\xf3n de los sensores de nivel alto de agua en sentina. Revisi\\xf3n funcional de la bomba autom\\xe1tica de achique y sus alarmas.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.title\": \"3. Salvamento y Electr\\xf3nica de Seguridad (LSA & GMDSS)\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item1.title\": \"Balsas Salvavidas de Recreo — ISO 9650\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item1.text\": \"Revisi\\xf3n certificada de balsas ISO 9650-1 y 9650-2 (Marcas homologadas: Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf). Servicio de recogida y entrega en pantal\\xe1n.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item2.title\": \"Radiobalizas EPIRB — Servicio Oficial ACR Electronics\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item2.text\": \"Cambio de bater\\xeda, sustituci\\xf3n de zafas hidrost\\xe1ticas y programaci\\xf3n de MMSI conforme a las autoridades mar\\xedtimas. Somos estaci\\xf3n de servicio oficial ACR Electronics.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item3.title\": \"Transpondedores AIS — Clase A y B\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item3.text\": \"Servicio t\\xe9cnico y configuraci\\xf3n de transpondedores AIS Clase A y Clase B. Programaci\\xf3n de MMSI, pruebas de recepci\\xf3n y transmisi\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item4.title\": \"Gesti\\xf3n de Pirotecnia Caducada\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item4.text\": \"Servicio profesional de retirada y destrucci\\xf3n certificada de pirotecnia caducada (bengalas de mano, cohetes paraca\\xeddas, botes de humo). Emitimos el certificado oficial de gesti\\xf3n de residuos peligrosos.\",\n        \"nr.sup.title\": \"Suministros — Venta, Repuestos y Avituallamiento\",\n        \"nr.sup1.title\": \"1. Equipamiento de Dise\\xf1o y Confort\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item1.title\": 'Extintores \"Yacht Line\" — Acabados Premium',\n        \"nr.sup1.item1.text\": \"Suministro de extintores con acabados premium que cumplen la normativa sin romper la est\\xe9tica: Cromado, Negro Mate, Blanco y Fibra de Carbono.\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item2.title\": \"Mantas Ign\\xedfugas — Formato Compacto para Galley\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item2.text\": \"Modelos en cajas r\\xedgidas ultra-compactas dise\\xf1adas para cocinas n\\xe1uticas (Galley). Cumplimiento normativo con m\\xednimo impacto visual.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.title\": \"2. Seguridad Personal (Life Saving)\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item1.title\": \"Chalecos Autoinflables de Alto Confort\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item1.text\": \"Venta de chalecos ergon\\xf3micos con arn\\xe9s integrado para navegaci\\xf3n a vela y regatas. Modelos Ocean, Coastal y Offshore seg\\xfan la zona de navegaci\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item2.title\": \"Dispositivos Hombre al Agua (MOB)\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item2.text\": \"Suministro de AIS-MOB personales que se integran en el chaleco salvavidas y transmiten autom\\xe1ticamente la posici\\xf3n al plotter.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item3.title\": \"Botiquines Reglamentarios y Ox\\xedgeno Medicinal\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item3.text\": \"Kits de primeros auxilios conforme a los requisitos de cada zona de navegaci\\xf3n. Botellas de ox\\xedgeno medicinal con mascarilla y regulador.\",\n        \"nr.sup3.title\": \"3. Pirotecnia y Supervivencia\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item1.title\": \"Kits de Se\\xf1ales Pirot\\xe9cnicas\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item1.text\": \"Bengalas de mano, cohetes paraca\\xeddas y botes de humo flotantes con aprobaci\\xf3n SOLAS o Marina Mercante seg\\xfan zona de navegaci\\xf3n.\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item2.title\": \"Accesorios de Balsa y Equipos de Supervivencia\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item2.text\": \"Grab-bags (bolsas de abandono) equipadas y personalizadas seg\\xfan la ruta de navegaci\\xf3n. Raciones de emergencia, agua potable desalinizadora y material de se\\xf1alizaci\\xf3n.\",\n        // ── INDUSTRIAL & COMERCIAL PAGE CONTENT ───────────────────\n        \"ic.page.subtitle\": \"La seguridad en una planta industrial o un complejo comercial no admite m\\xe1rgenes de error. En Extinval trasladamos la exigencia extrema, la disciplina y las certificaciones del sector mar\\xedtimo directamente a sus instalaciones en tierra.\",\n        \"ic.intro\": \"En Extinval no creemos que la seguridad en tierra sea una disciplina diferente a la seguridad mar\\xedtima — es la misma exigencia aplicada a un entorno diferente. Las mismas certificaciones IACS, los mismos protocolos de inspecci\\xf3n y la misma trazabilidad documental que blindan a sus buques ante el Port State Control son los que aplicamos en sus naves industriales, centros log\\xedsticos y edificios comerciales. Ofrecemos desde el mantenimiento de sistemas convencionales hasta la integraci\\xf3n de las tecnolog\\xedas m\\xe1s modernas y ecol\\xf3gicas del mercado.\",\n        \"ic.srv.title\": \"Servicios — Mantenimiento, Diagn\\xf3stico y Calibraci\\xf3n\",\n        \"ic.srv1.title\": \"1. Mantenimiento y Resoluci\\xf3n de Aver\\xedas FFE\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item1.title\": \"Mantenimiento Integral de Sistemas Fijos\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item1.text\": \"Revisiones preventivas y correctivas de sistemas fijos de extinci\\xf3n de incendios — rociadores, gases, espuma y polvo — en naves industriales, centros log\\xedsticos y edificios comerciales. Planificamos el mantenimiento para minimizar las interrupciones de su actividad productiva.\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item2.title\": \"Respuesta T\\xe9cnica y Resoluci\\xf3n de Aver\\xedas\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item2.text\": \"Diagn\\xf3stico r\\xe1pido y resoluci\\xf3n de aver\\xedas en sistemas cr\\xedticos para evitar paradas de producci\\xf3n o cierres de instalaciones por incumplimiento de seguridad. Tiempo de respuesta comprometido con contratos de mantenimiento. Disponibilidad 24/7 para instalaciones cr\\xedticas.\",\n        \"ic.srv2.title\": \"2. Detecci\\xf3n de Incendios y Alarmas\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item1.title\": \"Mantenimiento de Sistemas Centralizados de Detecci\\xf3n\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item1.text\": \"Verificaci\\xf3n de paneles de detecci\\xf3n y lazos en entornos industriales complejos: alta densidad de polvo, humedad extrema, altas temperaturas o atm\\xf3sferas corrosivas. Trabajamos con las principales marcas del mercado: Siemens, Honeywell, Hochiki, Apollo y Notifier.\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item2.title\": \"Auditor\\xeda de Sensibilidad — Sin Falsas Alarmas\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item2.text\": \"Pruebas funcionales de detectores de humo, calor y llama para asegurar una respuesta temprana sin falsas alarmas que paralicen la operativa diaria. Las falsas alarmas en entornos industriales tienen un coste econ\\xf3mico y de reputaci\\xf3n muy elevado — nuestro protocolo de auditor\\xeda elimina esta problem\\xe1tica de ra\\xedz.\",\n        \"ic.srv3.title\": \"3. Calibraci\\xf3n de Gases Industriales\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item1.title\": \"Control de Atm\\xf3sferas y Espacios Confinados\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item1.text\": \"Calibraci\\xf3n certificada de detectores de gas fijos y port\\xe1tiles — explos\\xedmetros, detectores de gases t\\xf3xicos y deficiencia de ox\\xedgeno — vitales para el personal de mantenimiento en silos, tanques de almacenamiento y plantas qu\\xedmicas. La normativa de espacios confinados exige calibraci\\xf3n con patrones verificados antes de cada entrada.\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item2.title\": \"Trazabilidad Total — Certificados para Inspecci\\xf3n\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item2.text\": \"Emisi\\xf3n de certificados de calibraci\\xf3n con patrones trazables a organismos nacionales (ENAC/PTB/NIST) para superar cualquier inspecci\\xf3n de la Administraci\\xf3n de Industria o de Riesgos Laborales. La misma trazabilidad documental que aplicamos en clasificaci\\xf3n mar\\xedtima, ahora disponible para su planta.\",\n        \"ic.sup.title\": \"Suministros — Innovaci\\xf3n, Venta y Reposici\\xf3n\",\n        \"ic.sup1.title\": \"1. Soluciones Ecol\\xf3gicas de Extinci\\xf3n — Vanguardia Tecnol\\xf3gica\",\n        \"ic.sup1.item1.title\": \"Aerosoles Condensados — La Tecnolog\\xeda m\\xe1s Avanzada\",\n        \"ic.sup1.item1.text\": \"Suministro e instalaci\\xf3n de la tecnolog\\xeda de extinci\\xf3n m\\xe1s avanzada y respetuosa con el medioambiente del mercado. Estos sistemas compactos ahogan el fuego a nivel molecular sin agotar el ox\\xedgeno de la sala, sin da\\xf1ar la electr\\xf3nica sensible y sin impacto en la capa de ozono. Ideales para salas de servidores, cuadros el\\xe9ctricos de alta tensi\\xf3n y centros de transformaci\\xf3n. No requieren obra civil — instalaci\\xf3n en un solo d\\xeda.\",\n        \"ic.sup2.title\": \"2. Sistemas de Detecci\\xf3n Inal\\xe1mbrica\",\n        \"ic.sup2.item1.title\": \"Detecci\\xf3n sin Cables — Sin Obra Civil\",\n        \"ic.sup2.item1.text\": \"Proveemos e instalamos sistemas de detecci\\xf3n de incendios inal\\xe1mbricos de \\xfaltima generaci\\xf3n. La soluci\\xf3n perfecta para naves industriales, edificios hist\\xf3ricos con protecci\\xf3n patrimonial o locales comerciales que necesitan actualizar su seguridad r\\xe1pidamente. Los tiempos de instalaci\\xf3n se reducen a la mitad frente a los sistemas cableados, sin necesidad de realizar obras civiles complejas ni rozas en paredes.\",\n        \"ic.sup3.title\": \"3. Equipamiento Convencional y Port\\xe1til\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item1.title\": \"Extintores de Alta Eficacia — Adaptados a su Carga de Fuego\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item1.text\": \"Venta y reposici\\xf3n de extintores de alta eficacia (Polvo ABC, CO₂, H\\xeddricos y Espuma) adaptados a la carga de fuego espec\\xedfica de su negocio y al tipo de materiales presentes en cada zona. Realizamos el estudio de la carga de fuego y determinamos el agente extintor \\xf3ptimo para cada \\xe1rea de su instalaci\\xf3n.\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item2.title\": \"Se\\xf1alizaci\\xf3n de Seguridad y Detecci\\xf3n Port\\xe1til\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item2.text\": \"Equipamiento complementario completo: se\\xf1alizaci\\xf3n fotoluminiscente de evacuaci\\xf3n y extinci\\xf3n, mantas ign\\xedfugas para cocinas industriales, detectores port\\xe1tiles de gas y CO para el personal de mantenimiento, y equipos de protecci\\xf3n respiratoria para espacios confinados.\"\n    },\n    en: {\n        // ── TOP BAR ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"topbar.emergency\": \"\",\n        \"topbar.about\": \"About Us\",\n        \"topbar.certs\": \"Certifications\",\n        \"topbar.contact\": \"Contact\",\n        \"topbar.clientArea\": \"Client Area →\",\n        // ── NAV ──────────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"nav.services\": \"Services\",\n        \"nav.oilGas\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"nav.merchant\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"nav.recreational\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"nav.industrial\": \"Industrial & Commercial\",\n        \"nav.about\": \"About\",\n        \"nav.authority\": \"Authority\",\n        \"nav.network\": \"Resources\",\n        \"nav.contact\": \"Contact\",\n        \"nav.cta\": \"Request a Proposal\",\n        // ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"hero.badge1\": \"Maritime & Industrial Safety \\xb7 Since 1980\",\n        \"hero.title1.l1\": \"INTEGRATED\",\n        \"hero.title1.l2\": \"SOLUTIONS IN\",\n        \"hero.title1.l3\": \"MARITIME\",\n        \"hero.title1.l4\": \"SAFETY\",\n        \"hero.lead1\": \"Over 40 years protecting lives and assets at sea. Oil & Gas, Merchant Fleet, Recreational Maritime and Industry with IACS approvals.\",\n        \"hero.cta1.primary\": \"Our Services\",\n        \"hero.cta1.secondary\": \"About Extinval\",\n        \"hero.badge2\": \"Merchant Vessels \\xb7 SOLAS / IMO\",\n        \"hero.title2.l1\": \"ZERO\",\n        \"hero.title2.l2\": \"DEFICIENCIES.\",\n        \"hero.title2.l3\": \"ZERO\",\n        \"hero.title2.l4\": \"DELAYS.\",\n        \"hero.lead2\": \"Full technical protection against Port State Control. Precision logistics adapted to your vessel's port call schedule.\",\n        \"hero.cta2.primary\": \"Merchant Division\",\n        \"hero.cta2.secondary\": \"IACS Approvals\",\n        \"hero.badge3\": \"Industrial & Commercial \\xb7 Naval Rigour Onshore\",\n        \"hero.title3.l1\": \"NAVAL\",\n        \"hero.title3.l2\": \"RIGOUR\",\n        \"hero.title3.l3\": \"APPLIED\",\n        \"hero.title3.l4\": \"ONSHORE.\",\n        \"hero.lead3\": \"We apply the extreme standards of the maritime sector to your industrial facilities. Condensed aerosols, wireless detection, full traceability.\",\n        \"hero.cta3.primary\": \"Industrial Solutions\",\n        \"hero.cta3.secondary\": \"Contact Us\",\n        // ── STATS STRIP ──────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"stats.years\": \"Years of Experience\",\n        \"stats.countries\": \"Countries with Own Office\",\n        \"stats.iacs\": \"IACS Approvals\",\n        \"stats.response\": \"Response Time\",\n        // ── TRUST BAR ────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"trust.label\": \"IACS Approvals\",\n        // ── DIVISIONES ───────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"div.overline\": \"Service Lines\",\n        \"div.title\": \"SPECIALISED DIVISIONS\",\n        \"div.lead\": \"Hyper-specialisation for every operating environment. The same IACS excellence applied with maximum technical precision.\",\n        \"srv1.title\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"srv1.sub\": \"Critical Risk\",\n        \"srv1.text\": \"Offshore platforms, Drillships and refineries. High-capacity FFE systems, ATEX calibration, LSA inspection and free-fall lifeboats.\",\n        \"srv1.cta\": \"Learn more\",\n        \"srv2.title\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"srv2.sub\": \"SOLAS / IMO\",\n        \"srv2.text\": \"Zero deficiencies against Port State Control. CO₂, Water Mist & Foam. Davit load testing. UTI calibration. OEM Hatecke & Global Davit.\",\n        \"srv2.cta\": \"Learn more\",\n        \"srv3.title\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"srv3.sub\": \"Excellence in Detail\",\n        \"srv3.text\": '\"White Glove\" service for Yachts & Superyachts. Novec 1230 clean agents. ISO 9650 liferafts. GMDSS: EPIRB, AIS, SART. Expired pyrotechnics management.',\n        \"srv3.cta\": \"Learn more\",\n        \"srv4.title\": \"Industrial & Commercial\",\n        \"srv4.sub\": \"Naval Rigour Onshore\",\n        \"srv4.text\": \"FFE maintenance in warehouses and logistics centres. Cutting-edge condensed aerosols. Wireless detection with no civil works. ATEX calibration.\",\n        \"srv4.cta\": \"Learn more\",\n        // ── CIFRAS ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"cifras.overline\": \"Track Record\",\n        \"cifras.title\": \"+40 YEARS SAFEGUARDING LIVES AT SEA\",\n        \"cifra1\": \"Years of Experience\",\n        \"cifra2\": \"Countries with Own Office\",\n        \"cifra3\": \"IACS Societies Approved\",\n        \"cifra4\": \"Global Response\",\n        // ── EJE SEGURIDAD ─────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"eje.overline\": \"Global Network\",\n        \"eje.title\": \"SECURITY AXIS\",\n        \"eje.lead\": \"Strategic coverage on the world's most critical trade routes. Spain, Canary Islands, Panama and North America.\",\n        \"eje.esp.name\": \"Spain\",\n        \"eje.esp.hq\": \"HQ\",\n        \"eje.esp.desc\": \"Central Headquarters in Valencia. Full coverage of the Mediterranean-Strait axis.\",\n        \"eje.cnr.name\": \"Canary Islands\",\n        \"eje.cnr.desc\": \"Mid-Atlantic Hub. Strategic position for trans-Atlantic traffic.\",\n        \"eje.pan.name\": \"Panama\",\n        \"eje.pan.desc\": \"Nerve centre of world trade. Critical services in the Canal, before and after transit.\",\n        \"eje.usa.name\": \"North America\",\n        \"eje.usa.desc\": \"Established presence on East, West and Gulf Coasts. Strict SOLAS compliance.\",\n        \"eje.mapLabel\": \"Direct Operation Points\",\n        \"eje.emergency.title\": \"DIRECT CONTACT\",\n        \"eje.emergency.sub\": \"Specialised technical team\",\n        // ── ABOUT ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"about.overline\": \"Who We Are\",\n        \"about.title\": \"HISTORY & MISSION\",\n        \"about.lead\": \"Extinval is synonymous with maritime safety on both sides of the Atlantic. Specialised in maintenance, inspection and supply of FFE and LSA systems.\",\n        \"about.quote\": \"We differentiate our service through three key pillars: Certified Excellence, Precision Logistics and Regulatory Compliance.\",\n        \"about.body\": \"Our structure provides expert response to three vital sectors: the critical operations of Merchant Vessels, large-scale Passenger safety, and the precision required by Recreational Maritime.\",\n        \"about.cta1\": \"About Extinval\",\n        \"about.cta2\": \"Request a Proposal\",\n        \"about.feat1.title\": \"Decentralised Stock\",\n        \"about.feat1.text\": \"OEM spare parts in Panama and US warehouses — minimal customs delays.\",\n        \"about.feat2.title\": \"Flying Squads\",\n        \"about.feat2.text\": \"Technical teams ready to deploy to any secondary port.\",\n        \"about.feat3.title\": \"Global Coordination\",\n        \"about.feat3.text\": \"A single point of contact for inspections across multiple ports.\",\n        // ── PORTFOLIO ────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"pt.overline\": \"Technical Capabilities\",\n        \"pt.title\": \"INSPECTION & MAINTENANCE SERVICES\",\n        \"pt.cta\": \"Request a Quote\",\n        // ── AUTORIDAD ────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"aut.overline\": \"Authority & Backing\",\n        \"aut.title\": \"THE PASSPORT TO OPERATE GLOBALLY\",\n        \"aut.lead\": \"In the maritime industry, trust is not asked for — it is demonstrated through audits. Every certificate we issue is a legal document valid before any PSC, RightShip or oil company Vetting.\",\n        \"aut1.title\": \"IACS Classification Societies\",\n        \"aut1.sub\": \"Top-Level Audit\",\n        \"aut1.text\": \"Procedures, technicians and facilities periodically audited. Your vessel's H&M insurance maintains full validity.\",\n        \"aut2.title\": \"Flag State Approvals\",\n        \"aut2.sub\": \"International Legal Competence\",\n        \"aut2.text\": 'We act as \"Approved Service Providers\" for maritime administrations covering the world\\'s largest tonnage.',\n        \"aut3.title\": \"Authorised OEM Partners\",\n        \"aut3.sub\": \"Direct Access to Original Technology\",\n        \"aut3.text\": \"Authorised Technical Service Agreements with manufacturers. Updated manuals and OEM spare parts with guaranteed traceability.\",\n        \"iso.text\": \"Our internal structure ensures full traceability of every inspection, from order receipt to final certificate issuance.\",\n        \"iso.cta\": \"View Certifications\",\n        // ── PARTNERS ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"partners.label\": \"Authorised Partners & Manufacturers\",\n        // ── CONTACT ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"contact.overline\": \"Global Network & Contact\",\n        \"contact.title\": \"LET'S DISCUSS YOUR SAFETY PROJECT\",\n        \"contact.lead\": \"Fill in the form and our technical team will get back to you within 24 hours.\",\n        \"contact.addr.label\": \"Headquarters\",\n        \"contact.phone.label\": \"Telephone\",\n        \"contact.email.label\": \"Email\",\n        \"contact.form.title\": \"Request a Technical Proposal\",\n        \"contact.form.name\": \"Name / Company *\",\n        \"contact.form.email\": \"Email *\",\n        \"contact.form.phone\": \"Phone (optional)\",\n        \"contact.form.vessel\": \"Vessel / ship name *\",\n        \"contact.form.location\": \"Location *\",\n        \"contact.form.div\": \"Division of Interest *\",\n        \"contact.form.msg\": \"Description of the vessel / installation and requirement...\",\n        \"contact.form.submit\": \"Send Request →\",\n        \"contact.form.sending\": \"Sending...\",\n        \"contact.form.ok.title\": \"✓ Request received successfully\",\n        \"contact.form.ok.body\": \"Our technical team will contact you within 24 hours.\",\n        \"contact.div.opt1\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"contact.div.opt2\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"contact.div.opt3\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"contact.div.opt4\": \"Industrial & Commercial\",\n        \"contact.div.opt5\": \"OEM Spare Parts\",\n        \"contact.info.title\": \"Contact Information\",\n        \"contact.hq.label\": \"Headquarters\",\n        \"contact.emerg.label\": \"Telephone\",\n        \"contact.email2.label\": \"General Email\",\n        \"contact.emerg.title\": \"DIRECT CONTACT\",\n        \"contact.emerg.sub\": \"Specialised technical team\",\n        \"contact.locations.title\": \"Our Offices\",\n        \"contact.note.principal\": \"Main\",\n        // ── FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"footer.tagline\": \"Safety. Service. Solutions. When safety is critical and time is limited, the answer is Extinval.\",\n        \"footer.services\": \"Services\",\n        \"footer.company\": \"Company\",\n        \"footer.contactTitle\": \"Global Contact\",\n        \"footer.nosotros\": \"About Us\",\n        \"footer.trayectoria\": \"History\",\n        \"footer.certs\": \"Certifications\",\n        \"footer.partners\": \"OEM Partners\",\n        \"footer.oem\": \"OEM Spare Parts\",\n        \"footer.clientArea\": \"Client Area\",\n        \"footer.faqs\": \"FAQs\",\n        \"footer.copy\": \"\\xa9 {year} Extinval Group. All rights reserved.\",\n        \"footer.legal\": \"Legal Notice\",\n        \"footer.privacy\": \"Privacy\",\n        \"footer.cookies\": \"Cookies\",\n        // ── PAGE HEROES ──────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"page.home\": \"Home\",\n        \"breadcrumb.services\": \"Services\",\n        \"related.title\": \"Other Divisions\",\n        \"related.cta\": \"Explore →\",\n        \"sidebar.cta.label\": \"Request a Technical Proposal\",\n        \"sidebar.badges.title\": \"Applicable Approvals\",\n        // ── ÁREA CLIENTES PAGE ────────────────────────────────────\n        \"ac.breadcrumb\": \"Client Area\",\n        \"ac.cta\": \"Request Access\",\n        // ── NOSOTROS PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"nos.overline1\": \"History\",\n        \"nos.overline2\": \"Precision Logistics\",\n        \"nos.overline3\": \"Value Proposition\",\n        \"nos.title\": \"About Us\",\n        \"nos.sub\": \"More than 40 years safeguarding lives at sea and on land. Extinval Group: Safety. Service. Solutions.\",\n        \"nos.h1\": \"OUR HISTORY\",\n        \"nos.p1\": \"Extinval is synonymous with naval safety on both sides of the Atlantic. Specialised in the maintenance, inspection and supply of FFE and LSA systems, we have grown alongside our clients, expanding our operations from Spain to the USA.\",\n        \"nos.p2\": \"Our structure provides expert response to three vital sectors: the critical operations of Merchant Vessels, mass safety on Passenger ships, and the precision required for Recreational Marine. We protect major assets and human lives with the same passion.\",\n        \"nos.quote\": \"More than 40 years safeguarding lives at sea.\",\n        \"nos.log.title\": \"WE MINIMISE FLEET DOWNTIME\",\n        \"nos.log1.t\": \"Decentralised Stock\",\n        \"nos.log1.d\": \"We maintain critical spare parts (OEM Hatecke/Global Davit, valves, foam concentrates) in our Panama and USA warehouses to reduce customs and shipping lead times.\",\n        \"nos.log2.t\": \"Flying Squads — Technical Mobility\",\n        \"nos.log2.d\": \"Our teams are ready to deploy to any secondary port within our areas of influence, ensuring vessels do not need to deviate from their route to receive service.\",\n        \"nos.log3.t\": \"Global Coordination\",\n        \"nos.log3.d\": \"A single point of contact to manage inspections across multiple ports. We plan your fleet's maintenance schedule in line with the natural stops on the commercial route.\",\n        \"nos.pv.title\": \"THREE GUARANTEES,\\nONE GLOBAL MISSION\",\n        \"nos.pv1.t\": \"Certified Excellence\",\n        \"nos.pv1.d\": \"IACS approvals with the five major classification societies. Official partners of manufacturers including ACR Electronics and Onguard. Every certificate issued is a legally watertight document.\",\n        \"nos.pv2.t\": \"Precision Logistics\",\n        \"nos.pv2.d\": \"Adapted to your vessel's port call schedule. Decentralised stock in Panama and the USA. Flying Squads deployable to any port within our areas of influence.\",\n        \"nos.pv3.t\": \"Regulatory Compliance\",\n        \"nos.pv3.d\": \"We protect your operations against any international inspection: Port State Control, RightShip and oil major Vetting. The same naval rigour, now also applied on land.\",\n        // ── AUTORIDAD PAGE ────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"aut.pg.overline\": \"Verified Competence\",\n        \"aut.rep.overline\": \"OEM Spare Parts\",\n        \"aut.iacs.sub\": \"Audited to the Highest Standard\",\n        \"aut.flag.sub\": \"International Legal Compliance\",\n        \"aut.oem.sub\": \"Direct Access to Original Technology\",\n        \"aut.iso.sub\": \"Certified Quality Management\",\n        \"aut.pg.title\": \"Authority Backing\",\n        \"aut.pg.sub\": \"The passport to operate globally. IACS certifications, Flag State approvals and OEM partners.\",\n        \"aut.pg.h2\": \"THE PASSPORT TO OPERATE GLOBALLY\",\n        \"aut.pg.lead\": \"In the maritime industry, trust is not requested; it is demonstrated through audits. Our technical competence is not a marketing promise — it is a fact validated by the world's most demanding bodies. Every certificate we issue is a legally watertight document against any PSC, RightShip or oil major Vetting.\",\n        \"aut.iacs.t\": \"Classification Societies (IACS)\",\n        \"aut.iacs.d\": \"Our procedures, technicians and facilities are periodically audited by IACS members. We operate under the strictest standards to ensure that your vessel's Hull & Machinery (H&M) insurance retains its full validity.\",\n        \"aut.flag.t\": \"Flag State Approvals\",\n        \"aut.flag.d\": 'We act as \"Approved Service Providers\" to the maritime administrations representing the largest tonnage of the world fleet. We certify equipment on vessels under strategic flags without geographical restrictions.',\n        \"aut.oem.t\": \"Manufacturer Approvals (OEM)\",\n        \"aut.oem.d\": \"Authorised Technical Service agreements with manufacturers. Access to up-to-date manuals, proprietary diagnostic software and genuine spare parts. Unlike generic multi-brand workshops, we are the direct link.\",\n        \"aut.iso.d\": \"Our internal structure is governed by integrated management systems that ensure traceability of every inspection, from order entry to final certificate issuance. Standardised excellence in every service.\",\n        \"aut.soc.overline\": \"International Certification\",\n        \"aut.soc.h2\": \"Classification Societies\",\n        \"aut.soc.lead\": \"Our facilities, technicians and procedures have been audited and approved by the five leading classification societies that are members of IACS.\",\n        \"aut.rep.title\": \"ORIGINAL SUPPLY:\\nTHE NO-DETENTION GUARANTEE\",\n        \"aut.rep.lead\": \"In the maritime sector, a non-conforming spare part can mean vessel detention. At Extinval we manage an exclusive Original Spare Parts (OEM) division with strategic stock in our Spain and USA warehouses.\",\n        \"aut.rep1.t\": \"Strategic Alliances — Lifeboats & Davits\",\n        \"aut.rep1.d\": \"Official partners of Hatecke and Global Davit. We eliminate intermediaries that increase cost and delay supply. Priority stock available in our Spain and USA warehouses.\",\n        \"aut.rep2.t\": \"FFE & Safety Supplies\",\n        \"aut.rep2.d\": \"20L containers of AFFF and AR-AFFF foam concentrates (Low and High expansion) with recent batch certification. Certified DCP dry chemical charges for fixed systems and portable extinguishers.\",\n        \"aut.rep3.t\": \"Electronics & Survival — ACR Electronics\",\n        \"aut.rep3.d\": \"Authorised service station for ACR Electronics EPIRB, PLB and SART. Distributors of Onguard systems. Rotating pyrotechnics stock to ensure maximum expiry dates.\",\n        // ── RED GLOBAL / RECURSOS PAGE ───────────────────────────\n        \"rg.breadcrumb\": \"Resources\",\n        \"rg.title\": \"Resources & Knowledge\",\n        \"rg.sub\": \"Strategic coverage on the world's most critical trade routes. The same level of technical excellence at every point around the globe.\",\n        \"rg.overline\": \"Security Axis\",\n        \"rg.h2\": \"STRATEGIC COVERAGE ON CRITICAL ROUTES\",\n        \"rg.mapLabel\": \"Direct Operation Points\",\n        \"rg.emerg.title\": \"DIRECT CONTACT\",\n        \"rg.emerg.sub\": \"Specialised technical team\",\n        \"rg.hq\": \"HQ\",\n        \"rg.loc.esp\": \"Spain\",\n        \"rg.loc.cnr\": \"Canary Islands\",\n        \"rg.loc.pan\": \"Panama\",\n        \"rg.loc.usa\": \"North America\",\n        \"rg.pin.hq\": \"HEADQUARTERS \\xb7 HQ\",\n        \"rg.pin.med\": \"Strait \\xb7 Mediterranean\",\n        \"rg.pin.atl\": \"Atlantic Hub\",\n        \"rg.pin.pan\": \"Panama\",\n        \"rg.pin.usa\": \"North America\",\n        \"nos.eje.lead\": \"Maritime safety knows no borders, and port call times leave no room for logistical errors. At Extinval Group we have designed our international expansion following the world's most demanding trade routes in key locations, such as the Mediterranean and the Panama Canal. We are not a scattered franchise network; we are a consolidated group with our own offices on the Atlantic and Pacific axis.\",\n        \"rg.blog.overline\": \"Technical Articles\",\n        \"rg.blog.h2\": \"RESOURCES & KNOWLEDGE\",\n        \"rg.blog.lead\": \"Technical analyses, regulatory guides and case studies prepared by our team of engineers specialising in maritime and industrial safety.\",\n        // ── CONTACTO PAGE ────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"ct.breadcrumb\": \"Contact\",\n        \"ct.title\": \"Global Contact\",\n        \"ct.sub\": \"Response within 24h. Our technical team will be in touch with you.\",\n        \"ct.form.overline\": \"Send Us a Message\",\n        \"ct.form.title\": \"REQUEST A TECHNICAL PROPOSAL\",\n        \"ct.form.name\": \"Name / Company *\",\n        \"ct.form.email\": \"Email *\",\n        \"ct.form.div\": \"Division of Interest *\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt1\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt2\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt3\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt4\": \"Industrial & Commercial\",\n        \"ct.form.div.opt5\": \"OEM Spare Parts\",\n        \"ct.form.msg\": \"Description of the vessel / installation and requirement...\",\n        \"ct.form.submit\": \"Send Request →\",\n        \"ct.form.sending\": \"Sending...\",\n        \"ct.form.ok\": \"✓ Request received successfully\",\n        \"ct.form.ok.body\": \"Our technical team will contact you within 24 hours.\",\n        \"ct.info.title\": \"Contact Information\",\n        \"ct.hq\": \"Headquarters\",\n        \"ct.emerg\": \"Telephone\",\n        \"ct.email\": \"General Email\",\n        \"ct.emerg.title\": \"DIRECT CONTACT\",\n        \"ct.emerg.sub\": \"Specialised technical team\",\n        \"ct.offices.title\": \"Our Offices\",\n        \"ct.offices.note\": \"Main\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"nr.badge\": \"Yachts & Superyachts \\xb7 Charter\",\n        \"nr.breadcrumb\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.title\": \"Need assistance for your yacht?\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.text\": \"Pontoon collection and on-board visit service available at our Valencia, Algeciras, Las Palmas and Canary Islands offices.\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.cta.btn\": \"Request On-Board Service\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.supply\": \"Featured Supplies\",\n        \"nr.sidebar.norm\": \"Applicable Regulations\",\n        \"nr.related.title\": \"Other Divisions\",\n        \"nr.sup4.title\": \"4. Ecological Fire Suppression Solutions — Cutting-Edge Technology\",\n        \"nr.sup4.item1.title\": \"Condensed Aerosols — The Most Advanced Technology\",\n        \"nr.sup4.item1.text\": \"Supply and installation of the most advanced and environmentally friendly fire suppression technology on the market. These compact systems extinguish fire at a molecular level without depleting the oxygen in the room, without damaging sensitive electronics and without any impact on the ozone layer.\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA SIDEBAR SUPPLY ITEMS ──────────────────────────\n        \"nr.supply.item1.title\": \"Yacht Line Extinguishers\",\n        \"nr.supply.item1.text\": \"Chrome, Matt Black, White, Carbon Fibre.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item2.title\": \"ISO 9650 Liferafts\",\n        \"nr.supply.item2.text\": \"Pontoon collection. Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item3.title\": \"EPIRB & AIS-MOB\",\n        \"nr.supply.item3.text\": \"Official ACR Electronics service.\",\n        \"nr.supply.item4.title\": \"Condensed Aerosols\",\n        \"nr.supply.item4.text\": \"Stat-X / FirePro. Eco-friendly technology, no pipework.\",\n        // ── SHARED BADGE LABELS ───────────────────────────────────\n        \"badge.islas.marshall\": \"Marshall Islands\",\n        \"badge.espana.ue\": \"Spain/EU\",\n        \"badge.marina.mercante\": \"Merchant Marine\",\n        \"badge.iso9650\": \"ISO 9650-1 & 9650-2\",\n        // ── FAQ PAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"faq.breadcrumb\": \"FAQs\",\n        \"faq.title\": \"Frequently Asked Questions\",\n        \"faq.sub\": \"Everything you need to know about our services, certifications and global coverage.\",\n        \"faq.tab.all\": \"All\",\n        \"faq.tab.buques\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"faq.tab.oilgas\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"faq.tab.nautica\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"faq.tab.industria\": \"Industry\",\n        // FAQ General\n        \"faq.gen.q1\": \"Where are Extinval's offices and technical headquarters located?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a1\": \"We have a network of our own offices and service centres to ensure global logistics coverage:\\n\\nHeadquarters (HQ): Carrer Serra d'Espad\\xe0, 28, Aldaia (Valencia, Spain).\\n\\nSpanish offices: Las Palmas de Gran Canaria and Almer\\xeda.\\n\\nUnited States: Offices in New Jersey (Harrison), Louisiana (Saint Rose), California (Alameda) and regional coverage from Houston/Miami.\\n\\nInternational Americas: Service centres in Panama and Canada.\",\n        \"faq.gen.q2\": \"What certifications underpin your inspection services?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a2\": \"Our processes operate under ISO 9001:2015 certification. We are audited and approved by the leading IACS classification societies: DNV, Lloyd's Register, Bureau Veritas (BV), ABS and RINA. This allows us to issue certificates valid for the most demanding flags (Spain/EU, Panama, Liberia, Bahamas, Marshall Islands).\",\n        \"faq.gen.q3\": \"How can I contact the technical team about an incident?\",\n        \"faq.gen.a3\": \"You can reach us directly by phone (+34 96 367 40 53) or email (service@extinval.com). Our technical team will handle your enquiry and get back to you as soon as possible.\",\n        // FAQ Merchant Vessels\n        \"faq.buques.q1\": \"How do you guarantee the vessel passes Port State Control (PSC) without detentions?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a1\": 'We apply a \"total technical protection\" protocol. We review and certify all survival (LSA) and fire-fighting (FFE) systems under strict SOLAS / IMO regulations, guaranteeing the operational readiness of equipment in the Engine Room, Deck and Bridge to ensure \"Zero Deficiencies\".',\n        \"faq.buques.q2\": \"Are you able to certify lifeboats and davits of Asian origin?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a2\": \"Absolutely. We carry out annual and five-yearly inspections (including structural load testing) being certified by leading European manufacturers (Hatecke, Global Davit) and major Asian Key Players (Jiangsu Jiaoyan, Shigi, Mansei, Oriental, Hyundai/Bada and Qingdao Beihai).\",\n        \"faq.buques.q3\": \"Is it possible to calibrate all equipment in a single on-board visit?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a3\": \"Yes. We optimise port call time by certifying in a single intervention gas detectors, breathalysers, pressure gauges and UTI (Interface/Temperature) gauges, providing full traceability for PSC and oil company vetting.\",\n        \"faq.buques.q4\": \"What happens if the vessel calls at a secondary port where Extinval has no office?\",\n        \"faq.buques.a4\": \"We deploy our Flying Squads — rapid-response technical teams who travel to the port of call. The vessel does not need to deviate from its commercial route, minimising downtime. We also hold decentralised OEM spare parts stock in Panama and the USA for fast shipments.\",\n        // FAQ Oil & Gas\n        \"faq.oilgas.q1\": \"Are you qualified to work in explosive atmospheres (ATEX)?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a1\": \"Yes. Our specialists manage and calibrate fixed sensor networks (LEL, H2S, CO, O2) and optical flame detectors (IR/UV) in ATEX environments. We also supply fleets of multi-gas detectors and intrinsically safe emergency communications (UHF/VHF Radios, PLB).\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q2\": \"What specific maintenance do fire suppression systems on platforms require?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a2\": \"We carry out comprehensive maintenance of large CO2 banks, clean agent systems (Novec 1230 / Inergen) and fluidisation and line purging tests on large fixed powder stations (Skids) designed to combat high-pressure gas fires (Jet Fires).\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q3\": \"Is it mandatory to analyse the foam concentrates in deluge systems?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a3\": \"Yes, it is a regulatory requirement. We carry out laboratory chemical analysis of foam concentrates (AR-AFFF) subjected to extreme marine conditions. We also have the capacity for immediate supply of new fluorine-free formulas (SFFF) in 1,000L IBC format.\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.q4\": \"How do you protect personnel against leaks of lethal gases such as H2S?\",\n        \"faq.oilgas.a4\": \"We supply emergency escape breathing devices (EEBD) and carry out maintenance of breathable air cascade systems (Air Cascade Systems). We certify high-pressure compressors under EN 12021 to guarantee 100% safe air in confined spaces.\",\n        // FAQ Recreational Maritime\n        \"faq.nautica.q1\": 'What does the \"White Glove\" approach mean for your on-board inspections?',\n        \"faq.nautica.a1\": \"We understand that aesthetics are fundamental on a superyacht. Our staff carefully protects teak decks and premium interiors during the inspection of extinguishers and fixed systems (FFE), guaranteeing a clean intervention with no visual impact.\",\n        \"faq.nautica.q2\": \"Are there fire extinguishers that comply with regulations without altering the yacht's design?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a2\": 'Yes, we stock the \"Yacht Line\" collection. These are high-efficacy extinguishers with premium finishes (Chrome, Matt Black, White and Carbon Fibre) designed to integrate perfectly with the aesthetics of luxury saloons and cabins.',\n        \"faq.nautica.q3\": \"Which fixed systems do you recommend to protect the engine room without damaging the engines?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a3\": \"We recommend and install clean agents (Novec 1230, FM-200 or HFC-227ea) or ultra-compact aerosol generators (Stat-X / FirePro). These systems extinguish fire without leaving residues harmful to high-value electronics or machinery.\",\n        \"faq.nautica.q4\": \"What life-saving (LSA) and safety electronics equipment do you manage?\",\n        \"faq.nautica.a4\": \"We inspect ISO 9650 liferafts (brands such as Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf) with a pontoon collection service. As an official ACR Electronics service station, we also certify EPIRBs, PLBs and AIS transponders (Class A and B), and handle certified disposal of expired pyrotechnics.\",\n        // FAQ Industrial\n        \"faq.industrial.q1\": \"What does a maritime sector company bring to an industrial land-based installation?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a1\": \"We transfer the extreme discipline, certifications and documentary traceability demanded by maritime regulations (IACS) to chemical plants, logistics warehouses and data centres. This ensures that sprinkler, powder or foam systems offer maximum reliability onshore.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q2\": \"How do you prevent false alarms that cause production stoppages?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a2\": \"We conduct Sensitivity Audits on centralised detection systems (Siemens, Honeywell, Hochiki, Apollo, Notifier) to ensure early response to real fires without false alarms caused by dust, humidity or high industrial temperatures.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q3\": \"Is it possible to upgrade the fire system in my premises without civil construction works?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a3\": \"Yes. We install wireless detection systems that require no cables or wall routing, reducing installation time by half. We also implement Condensed Aerosols — a molecular suppression technology with no ecological impact that can be installed in a single day without pipework.\",\n        \"faq.industrial.q4\": \"Are gas detector calibrations carried out in industry legally valid?\",\n        \"faq.industrial.a4\": \"Absolutely. We issue calibration certificates for confined spaces with standards traceable to national and international bodies (ENAC / PTB / NIST), ensuring your company passes any inspection by Industry or Occupational Risk authorities.\",\n        // ── HERO SLIDES ──────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"slide1.division\": \"Oil & Gas\",\n        \"slide1.claim1\": \"MAXIMUM RELIABILITY\",\n        \"slide1.claim2\": \"IN CRITICAL RISK ENVIRONMENTS\",\n        \"slide1.lead\": \"Offshore platforms, Drillships and refineries. High-capacity FFE systems, ATEX calibration and LSA inspection under IACS standards.\",\n        \"slide2.division\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"slide2.claim1\": \"ZERO\",\n        \"slide2.claim2\": \"DEFICIENCIES.\",\n        \"slide2.claim3\": \"ZERO DELAYS.\",\n        \"slide2.lead\": \"Full technical protection against Port State Control. Precision logistics adapted to your vessel's port call schedule.\",\n        \"slide3.division\": \"Recreational Maritime\",\n        \"slide3.claim1\": \"SAIL\",\n        \"slide3.claim2\": \"WITHOUT WORRY,\",\n        \"slide3.claim3\": \"PERIOD.\",\n        \"slide3.subtitle\": \"Aesthetics and functionality\",\n        \"slide3.lead\": '\"White Glove\" service for Yachts, Superyachts and Charter. Maximum discretion, minimal visual impact.',\n        \"slide4.division\": \"Industrial & Commercial\",\n        \"slide4.claim1\": \"NAVAL RIGOUR\",\n        \"slide4.claim2\": \"APPLIED TO\",\n        \"slide4.claim3\": \"ONSHORE INDUSTRY.\",\n        \"slide4.lead\": \"We apply the extreme standards of the maritime sector to your facilities. Condensed aerosols, wireless detection, full traceability.\",\n        // ── PORTFOLIO ITEMS ───────────────────────────────────────\n        \"pt1.cat\": \"FFE — Suppression\",\n        \"pt1.name\": \"Fixed CO₂, Foam & Mist Systems\",\n        \"pt1.desc\": \"Annual and five-yearly IACS inspection. AR-AFFF laboratory analysis.\",\n        \"pt2.cat\": \"LSA — Rescue\",\n        \"pt2.name\": \"Free-fall Lifeboats & Davits\",\n        \"pt2.desc\": \"Hatecke, Global Davit, Jiangsu Jiaoyan. Certified load testing.\",\n        \"pt3.cat\": \"ATEX — Detection\",\n        \"pt3.name\": \"Gas Calibration H₂S / LEL\",\n        \"pt3.desc\": \"Traceable certificates for PSC and oil company vetting.\",\n        \"pt4.cat\": \"Maritime\",\n        \"pt4.name\": \"ISO Liferafts & Pyrotechnics\",\n        \"pt4.desc\": \"ISO 9650. Certified management of expired pyrotechnics.\",\n        \"pt5.cat\": \"GMDSS / Radio\",\n        \"pt5.name\": \"EPIRB \\xb7 AIS \\xb7 SART\",\n        \"pt5.desc\": \"Official ACR Electronics service. MMSI programming.\",\n        \"pt6.cat\": \"Industrial\",\n        \"pt6.name\": \"Aerosols & Wireless Detection\",\n        \"pt6.desc\": \"Molecular suppression. No civil works. Eco-friendly technology.\",\n        \"pt7.cat\": \"OEM Parts\",\n        \"pt7.name\": \"Strategic Stock ESP/USA\",\n        \"pt7.desc\": \"Official distribution: Hatecke, Global Davit, Viking, Zodiac.\",\n        // ── ISO STRIP ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n        \"iso.sub\": \"Certified Quality Management\",\n        // ── RELATED CARD DESCRIPTIONS ─────────────────────────────\n        \"related.og.d\": \"Maximum reliability in offshore and critical risk environments.\",\n        \"related.bm.d\": \"Zero deficiencies before Port State Control. SOLAS / IMO.\",\n        \"related.nr.d\": '\"White Glove\" service for Yachts and Superyachts.',\n        \"related.ic.d\": \"Naval rigour applied to industrial installations onshore.\",\n        // ── OIL & GAS PAGE CHROME ─────────────────────────────────\n        \"og.badge\": \"Critical Sector — Offshore & Refineries\",\n        \"og.sidebar.title\": \"Need technical assistance?\",\n        \"og.sidebar.text\": \"Our O&G specialists are ready to handle any incident on a platform, Drillship or refinery.\",\n        \"og.sidebar.btn\": \"Contact Us\",\n        \"og.sidebar.supply\": \"OEM Supply Capacity\",\n        \"og.sup1.title\": \"AR-AFFF Foam Concentrates\",\n        \"og.sup1.text\": \"1,000L IBCs. Fluorine-free (SFFF) available.\",\n        \"og.sup2.title\": \"Multigas ATEX/IECEx\",\n        \"og.sup2.text\": \"4–6 gas. Detectors for operators.\",\n        \"og.sup3.title\": \"ATEX Radios\",\n        \"og.sup3.text\": \"Intrinsically safe UHF/VHF. PLBs.\",\n        \"og.sup4.title\": \"Offshore PPE\",\n        \"og.sup4.text\": \"SCBA, EEBDs, SOLAS Suits, Ground Monitors.\",\n        // ── BUQUES MERCANTES PAGE CHROME ──────────────────────────\n        \"bm.badge\": \"SOLAS / IMO — Regulatory Compliance\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.title\": \"Vessel in port?\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.text\": \"We minimise downtime. Our Flying Squads travel to your vessel at berth. A single point of contact for all inspections.\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.btn\": \"Contact Us\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.logistics\": \"Precision Logistics\",\n        \"bm.log1.title\": \"Decentralised Stock\",\n        \"bm.log1.text\": \"OEM spare parts in Panama and the USA — minimal customs and shipping delays.\",\n        \"bm.log2.title\": \"Flying Squads\",\n        \"bm.log2.text\": \"Technical teams to any secondary port. The vessel does not need to deviate.\",\n        \"bm.log3.title\": \"Global Coordination\",\n        \"bm.log3.text\": \"A single point of contact for the entire fleet and multiple ports.\",\n        \"bm.sidebar.approvals\": \"Approvals\",\n        // ── INDUSTRIAL & COMERCIAL PAGE CHROME ────────────────────\n        \"ic.badge\": \"Naval Rigour Onshore\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.title\": \"Need a diagnosis?\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.text\": \"We carry out a free audit of your current installation and present a maintenance plan tailored to your needs and budget.\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.btn\": \"Request Audit\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.tech\": \"Featured Technologies\",\n        \"ic.tech1.title\": \"Condensed Aerosols\",\n        \"ic.tech1.text\": \"Molecular suppression. No electronic damage. No civil works.\",\n        \"ic.tech2.title\": \"Wireless Detection\",\n        \"ic.tech2.text\": \"No cables, no works. Installation in one day.\",\n        \"ic.tech3.title\": \"ATEX Calibration\",\n        \"ic.tech3.text\": \"Traceable certificates ENAC/PTB/NIST.\",\n        \"ic.tech4.title\": \"Extinguishers\",\n        \"ic.tech4.text\": \"Powder, CO₂, Water, Foam. Adapted per zone.\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.adv\": \"Competitive Advantage\",\n        \"ic.adv1.label\": \"LR \\xb7 RINA \\xb7 DNV \\xb7 ABS \\xb7 BV\",\n        \"ic.adv1.text\": \"The same maritime certifications applied onshore\",\n        \"ic.adv2.label\": \"ISO 9001:2015\",\n        \"ic.adv2.text\": \"Full traceability of every intervention\",\n        \"ic.adv3.label\": \"Technical Response\",\n        \"ic.adv3.text\": \"For critical installations with a maintenance contract\",\n        \"ic.sidebar.sectors\": \"Sectors We Serve\",\n        \"ic.sector1\": \"Industrial Warehouses\",\n        \"ic.sector2\": \"Logistics Centres\",\n        \"ic.sector3\": \"Commercial Buildings\",\n        \"ic.sector4\": \"Chemical Plants\",\n        \"ic.sector5\": \"Data Centres\",\n        \"ic.sector6\": \"Hospitals\",\n        \"ic.sector7\": \"Historic Buildings\",\n        \"ic.sector8\": \"Retail Sector\",\n        // ── OIL & GAS PAGE CONTENT ────────────────────────────────\n        \"og.subtitle\": \"Maximum Reliability in Critical Risk Environments. Offshore platforms, Drillships and refineries.\",\n        \"og.intro\": \"The Oil & Gas sector operates under the most uncompromising safety standards in the world. A technical failure on an offshore platform, a drilling vessel (Drillship) or a refinery is not an option. Extinval brings our full engineering capacity to guarantee the protection of high-value assets and, above all, the lives of personnel in explosive atmospheres and hostile environments.\",\n        \"og.srv.title\": \"Inspection & Maintenance Services (FFE & LSA)\",\n        \"og.s1.title\": \"1. High-Capacity Fixed Fire Suppression Systems (FFE)\",\n        \"og.s1.i1.t\": \"Foam, Deluge & Dry Powder Systems\",\n        \"og.s1.i1.d\": \"Maintenance in process areas. Mandatory laboratory chemical analysis of foam concentrates (AR-AFFF) subjected to extreme marine conditions. Inspection of large fixed powder stations (Skids) vital for extinguishing high-pressure gas fires (Jet Fires). Fluidisation and line purging tests.\",\n        \"og.s1.i2.t\": \"CO₂ Banks & Clean Agents (Novec 1230 / Inergen)\",\n        \"og.s1.i2.d\": \"Inspection of large CO₂ banks for turbine and generator rooms. Novec 1230 and Inergen clean agent systems for protection of central control rooms (CCR) and critical electrical cabinets.\",\n        \"og.s2.title\": \"2. Gas Detection & Hazardous Atmospheres (ATEX)\",\n        \"og.s2.i1.t\": \"Fixed Sensor Networks on Plant — LEL, H₂S, CO, O₂\",\n        \"og.s2.i1.d\": \"Maintenance and calibration with reference gas of fixed sensor networks: Combustible Gases (LEL), Hydrogen Sulphide (H₂S, the deadliest risk in O&G), Carbon Monoxide (CO) and Oxygen deficiency. Full certificate traceability.\",\n        \"og.s2.i2.t\": \"Optical Flame Detectors IR/UV/CCTV\",\n        \"og.s2.i2.d\": \"Functional testing of optical detectors designed not to generate false alarms from sunlight or sea reflections. Calibration with certified reference sources.\",\n        \"og.s3.title\": \"3. Offshore Evacuation & Survival (LSA)\",\n        \"og.s3.i1.t\": \"Free-fall Lifeboats\",\n        \"og.s3.i1.d\": \"Annual and five-yearly inspection of hydraulic and structural release systems for rapid evacuation lifeboats. Personnel Transfer Systems: inspection of nets, transfer baskets (Frog/Billy Pugh) and davit-launched liferafts.\",\n        \"og.s3.i2.t\": \"Survival Suits & SCBA System Inspection\",\n        \"og.s3.i2.d\": \"Pressure and integrity tests for immersion and survival suits adapted to the petroleum industry. Maintenance of air supply units (Air Cascade Systems) for confined space work.\",\n        \"og.s4.title\": \"4. Life Support & Air Quality\",\n        \"og.s4.i1.t\": \"Cascade Systems & Breathable Air\",\n        \"og.s4.i1.d\": \"Maintenance of mobile and fixed air supply units (Air Cascade Systems) for confined space work. Certification of high-pressure compressors to EN 12021 / CGA G-7.1 to guarantee that the air in SCBA equipment and escape hoods is 100% safe.\",\n        \"og.sup.title\": \"Supplies — Technology, OEM Spare Parts & ATEX Safety\",\n        \"og.sup1.h\": \"1. High-Performance Extinguishing Agents\",\n        \"og.sup1.i1.t\": \"Special Foam Concentrates (SFFF & AR-AFFF)\",\n        \"og.sup1.i1.d\": \"Supply of fluorine-free (SFFF) and alcohol-resistant (AR-AFFF) foam concentrates in large volumes — drums and 1,000L IBCs — for immediate replenishment after an emergency or test.\",\n        \"og.sup1.i2.t\": \"Superior Grade Dry Chemical Powder\",\n        \"og.sup1.i2.d\": \"Silicone-treated dry chemical powder (DCP) to prevent compaction from platform vibrations. Certified charges for fixed systems and portable extinguishers.\",\n        \"og.sup2.h\": \"2. ATEX Equipment & Portable Detection\",\n        \"og.sup2.i1.t\": \"Portable Multi-gas Detectors (ATEX / IECEx)\",\n        \"og.sup2.i1.d\": \"Sale and supply of personal 4–6 gas detector fleets for operators, with intrinsically safe ATEX/IECEx certifications. Periodic calibration contract management included.\",\n        \"og.sup2.i2.t\": \"Emergency Communications — ATEX Radios & PLBs\",\n        \"og.sup2.i2.d\": \"Supply of intrinsically safe UHF/VHF radios and personal locator beacons (PLB) for deck personnel in areas with potentially explosive atmospheres.\",\n        \"og.sup3.h\": \"3. Respiratory Protection & Firefighting\",\n        \"og.sup3.i1.t\": \"H₂S Escape Equipment (EEBD) & Heavy Equipment\",\n        \"og.sup3.i1.d\": \"Quick-release escape hoods specifically for toxic gas leak emergencies. Wheeled mobile extinguishers (up to 135L or 50kg) with marine coatings to withstand extreme salt corrosion.\",\n        \"og.sup3.i2.t\": \"High-flow Water/Foam Monitors (Ground Monitors)\",\n        \"og.sup3.i2.d\": \"Portable high-flow monitors for rapid deployment in process areas. First-line defensive strategy against large-scale platform fires.\",\n        // ── BUQUES MERCANTES PAGE CONTENT ─────────────────────────\n        \"bm.title\": \"Merchant Vessels\",\n        \"bm.subtitle\": \"Zero Deficiencies. Zero Delays. Full technical protection against Port State Control for cargo ships, tankers, bulk carriers and container vessels.\",\n        \"bm.intro\": \"Our merchant division is designed to provide full technical protection for cargo ships, tankers, bulk carriers and container vessels. We understand the pressure of Port State Control; our protocols ensure the complete operational readiness of critical systems in the Engine Room, Deck and Bridge.\",\n        \"bm.srv.title\": \"Inspection & Maintenance Services (FFE & LSA)\",\n        \"bm.s1.title\": \"1. Fixed Fire Suppression Systems\",\n        \"bm.s1.i1.t\": \"CO₂ (+200 cylinders), Water Mist & Foam\",\n        \"bm.s1.i1.d\": \"Annual and five-yearly inspection of CO₂ systems (scalable to over 200 cylinders), Water Mist and Low/High-expansion Foam. Mandatory laboratory analysis of foam concentrates subjected to extreme marine conditions.\",\n        \"bm.s1.i2.t\": \"Water Mist for Engine Room & Galley\",\n        \"bm.s1.i2.d\": \"Inspection of water mist systems for protection of the engine room, deep fat fryers and high-risk cargo spaces. Verification of activation pressures and nozzles.\",\n        \"bm.s2.title\": \"2. Lifeboats & Davits — Load Testing\",\n        \"bm.s2.i1.t\": \"Certified Leading Manufacturers — Europe & Asia\",\n        \"bm.s2.i1.d\": \"Annual and five-yearly inspection with IACS and Flag/Class approvals. Europe: Hatecke, Global Davit. Asian Key Players: Jiangsu Jiaoyan, Shigi, Mansei, Oriental, Hyundai Lifeboats (Bada), Qingdao Beihai.\",\n        \"bm.s2.i2.t\": \"Structural Load Testing — Cranes, Davits & Gangways\",\n        \"bm.s2.i2.d\": \"Structural certification of provision cranes and davits. Critical inspection of gangways and accommodation ladders. Full documentation for PSC and IACS.\",\n        \"bm.s3.title\": \"3. Calibration & Instrumentation in a Single Visit\",\n        \"bm.s3.i1.t\": \"Gas Detectors, Breathalysers, Pressure Gauges & UTI\",\n        \"bm.s3.i1.d\": \"Comprehensive service in a single on-board visit: gas detectors, breathalysers, pressure gauges and UTI (Interface/Temperature) gauges. Certificates with full traceability for PSC and oil company vetting.\",\n        \"bm.s3.i2.t\": \"Breathable Air — EEBD, SCBA & Compressors\",\n        \"bm.s3.i2.d\": \"Compressor air quality to EN 12021. Inspection of EEBD (Emergency Escape Breathing Devices) for rapid evacuation. SCBA equipment review for the on-board fire brigade.\",\n        \"bm.sup.title\": \"Supplies — Sales, OEM Spare Parts & Provisioning\",\n        \"bm.sup1.title\": \"1. Original Spare Parts (OEM Parts)\",\n        \"bm.sup1.i1.t\": \"LSA Components for Hatecke & Global Davit\",\n        \"bm.sup1.i1.d\": \"Official spare parts distribution: steel cables, hydrostatic release hooks, davit motor components. Full traceability from manufacturer to vessel deck. No intermediaries that increase cost and delay supply.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.title\": \"2. Fire-fighting Equipment (FFE)\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i1.t\": \"Large-capacity Extinguishers — Powder & Foam\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i1.d\": \"Mobile trolleys of Powder (50kg) and Foam (45L / 135L) for deck and engine room. Marine corrosion-resistant coatings for maximum durability in salt environments.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i2.t\": \"Hoses, Nozzles & International Couplings\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i2.d\": \"High-pressure hoses, dual-effect nozzles and international couplings (Storz, Nakajima, Barcelona). SOLAS-certified fire axes and forcible entry tools.\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i3.t\": \"Extinguishing Agents — Certified Foam & Powder\",\n        \"bm.sup2.i3.d\": \"Drums of certified foam concentrate (AFFF and AR-AFFF) with the latest expiry dates. DCP dry chemical charges for fixed systems and portable extinguishers. Available for direct on-board delivery at our operating ports.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.title\": \"3. Personal Safety & Protection\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i1.t\": \"Technical Suits — Firefighting, Chemical & Immersion\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i1.d\": \"Firefighting suits (SOLAS), chemical protection suits and certified immersion suits. Crew equipment and spares for the on-board fire brigade.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i2.t\": \"New SCBA Sets, Cylinders & EEBDs\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i2.d\": \"Sale of complete next-generation SCBA sets. Replacement cylinders (6L and 9L). Quick-escape EEBD units for evacuation points in the engine room and confined spaces.\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i3.t\": \"Portable Detectors — Combustible Gas & Multi-gas\",\n        \"bm.sup3.i3.d\": \"Supply of next-generation combustible gas and multi-gas detectors for deck personnel and confined space operations. Periodic calibration contract available.\",\n        // ── NÁUTICA DE RECREO PAGE CONTENT ────────────────────────\n        \"nr.page.subtitle\": 'A \"White Glove\" service for Yachts, Superyachts and Charter. We handle the regulatory complexity so the owner can focus on enjoying the sea.',\n        \"nr.intro\": 'At Extinval we understand that a yacht or superyacht is the perfect combination of the pleasure of sailing and the strictest safety responsibility. Unlike conventional maintenance services, our \"White Glove\" approach protects the aesthetics of your vessel during every intervention, ensuring that regulatory inspections leave no mark on your interior spaces or teak deck. Maximum safety, minimal visual impact.',\n        \"nr.srv.title\": \"Maintenance, Inspection & Certification Services\",\n        \"nr.srv1.title\": '1. \"Clean & Safe\" Fire Protection (FFE)',\n        \"nr.srv1.item1.title\": \"Clean Agent Systems\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item1.text\": \"Maintenance and recharge of automatic fire suppression systems in engine rooms using Novec 1230, FM-200 or HFC-227ea gases. These agents extinguish fire without leaving residues, protecting the yacht's high-value electronics and engines.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item2.title\": \"Aerosol Generators (Stat-X / FirePro)\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item2.text\": \"Inspection of compact suppression systems that activate thermally or electrically, ideal for confined spaces on sailing yachts and motorboats. No pipework or pressurised agents required.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item3.title\": 'Portable Extinguishers — \"White Glove\" Inspection',\n        \"nr.srv1.item3.text\": \"Careful inspection of powder, foam and CO₂ extinguishers. We protect teak decks and premium interiors throughout the inspection. Chrome, matt black and carbon fibre finishes available.\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item4.title\": \"Shutdown Systems & Fire Dampers\",\n        \"nr.srv1.item4.text\": \"Verification of automatic shut-off of fuel valves and fans (Fire Dampers) when suppression is activated, in accordance with the requirements of the navigation zone.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.title\": \"2. Gas Detection & Environmental Safety\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item1.title\": \"Heavy LPG / Butane Gases in Bilges\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item1.text\": \"Installation and calibration of sensors in bilges (where heavy gas accumulates) to prevent explosions in galley areas and generator spaces.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item2.title\": \"Carbon Monoxide (CO) in Cabins\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item2.text\": \"Inspection of CO detectors in cabins, vital to prevent silent poisoning from poor combustion of generators or auxiliary engines.\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item3.title\": \"Bilge Alarms & Level Sensors\",\n        \"nr.srv2.item3.text\": \"Verification of high bilge water level sensors. Functional review of the automatic bilge pump and its alarms.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.title\": \"3. Life-saving & Safety Electronics (LSA & GMDSS)\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item1.title\": \"Recreational Liferafts — ISO 9650\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item1.text\": \"Certified inspection of ISO 9650-1 and 9650-2 liferafts (Approved brands: Almara Live, Neptuno, Seawolf). Pontoon collection and delivery service.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item2.title\": \"EPIRBs — Official ACR Electronics Service\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item2.text\": \"Battery replacement, hydrostatic release unit replacement and MMSI programming in accordance with maritime authorities. We are an official ACR Electronics service station.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item3.title\": \"AIS Transponders — Class A & B\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item3.text\": \"Technical service and configuration of Class A and Class B AIS transponders. MMSI programming, reception and transmission tests.\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item4.title\": \"Expired Pyrotechnics Management\",\n        \"nr.srv3.item4.text\": \"Professional collection and certified destruction of expired pyrotechnics (hand flares, parachute rockets, smoke signals). We issue the official hazardous waste management certificate.\",\n        \"nr.sup.title\": \"Supplies — Sales, Spare Parts & Provisioning\",\n        \"nr.sup1.title\": \"1. Design & Comfort Equipment\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item1.title\": '\"Yacht Line\" Extinguishers — Premium Finishes',\n        \"nr.sup1.item1.text\": \"Supply of extinguishers with premium finishes that comply with regulations without compromising aesthetics: Chrome, Matt Black, White and Carbon Fibre.\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item2.title\": \"Fire Blankets — Compact Format for Galley\",\n        \"nr.sup1.item2.text\": \"Models in ultra-compact rigid cases designed for marine galleys. Regulatory compliance with minimal visual impact.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.title\": \"2. Personal Safety (Life Saving)\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item1.title\": \"High-Comfort Self-inflating Lifejackets\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item1.text\": \"Sale of ergonomic lifejackets with integrated harness for sailing and racing. Ocean, Coastal and Offshore models according to navigation zone.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item2.title\": \"Man Overboard Devices (MOB)\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item2.text\": \"Supply of personal AIS-MOB units that integrate into the lifejacket and automatically transmit position to the chartplotter.\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item3.title\": \"Regulation First-aid Kits & Medical Oxygen\",\n        \"nr.sup2.item3.text\": \"First-aid kits compliant with the requirements of each navigation zone. Medical oxygen cylinders with mask and regulator.\",\n        \"nr.sup3.title\": \"3. Pyrotechnics & Survival\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item1.title\": \"Pyrotechnic Signal Kits\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item1.text\": \"Hand flares, parachute rockets and floating smoke signals with SOLAS or Merchant Marine approval depending on navigation zone.\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item2.title\": \"Liferaft Accessories & Survival Equipment\",\n        \"nr.sup3.item2.text\": \"Equipped and customised grab-bags according to the navigation route. Emergency rations, desalinating drinking water and signalling equipment.\",\n        // ── INDUSTRIAL & COMERCIAL PAGE CONTENT ───────────────────\n        \"ic.page.subtitle\": \"Safety in an industrial plant or commercial complex admits no margin for error. At Extinval we bring the extreme rigour, discipline and certifications of the maritime sector directly to your onshore installations.\",\n        \"ic.intro\": \"At Extinval we do not believe that onshore safety is a different discipline from maritime safety — it is the same rigour applied to a different environment. The same IACS certifications, the same inspection protocols and the same documentary traceability that protect your vessels against Port State Control are what we apply to your industrial warehouses, logistics centres and commercial buildings. We offer everything from conventional system maintenance to the integration of the most modern and eco-friendly technologies on the market.\",\n        \"ic.srv.title\": \"Services — Maintenance, Diagnosis & Calibration\",\n        \"ic.srv1.title\": \"1. FFE Maintenance & Fault Resolution\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item1.title\": \"Comprehensive Fixed System Maintenance\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item1.text\": \"Preventive and corrective inspections of fixed fire suppression systems — sprinklers, gases, foam and powder — in industrial warehouses, logistics centres and commercial buildings. We plan maintenance to minimise disruption to your productive activity.\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item2.title\": \"Technical Response & Fault Resolution\",\n        \"ic.srv1.item2.text\": \"Rapid diagnosis and fault resolution in critical systems to prevent production stoppages or facility closures due to safety non-compliance. Committed response times with maintenance contracts. 24/7 availability for critical installations.\",\n        \"ic.srv2.title\": \"2. Fire Detection & Alarms\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item1.title\": \"Centralised Detection System Maintenance\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item1.text\": \"Verification of detection panels and loops in complex industrial environments: high dust density, extreme humidity, high temperatures or corrosive atmospheres. We work with the leading market brands: Siemens, Honeywell, Hochiki, Apollo and Notifier.\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item2.title\": \"Sensitivity Audit — No False Alarms\",\n        \"ic.srv2.item2.text\": \"Functional testing of smoke, heat and flame detectors to ensure early response to real fires without false alarms that disrupt daily operations. False alarms in industrial environments have a very high economic and reputational cost — our audit protocol eliminates this problem at source.\",\n        \"ic.srv3.title\": \"3. Industrial Gas Calibration\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item1.title\": \"Atmosphere Control & Confined Spaces\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item1.text\": \"Certified calibration of fixed and portable gas detectors — combustible gas detectors, toxic gas detectors and oxygen deficiency monitors — vital for maintenance personnel in silos, storage tanks and chemical plants. Confined space regulations require calibration with verified standards before each entry.\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item2.title\": \"Full Traceability — Certificates for Inspection\",\n        \"ic.srv3.item2.text\": \"Issuance of calibration certificates with standards traceable to national bodies (ENAC/PTB/NIST) to pass any inspection by the Industry Administration or Occupational Risk authorities. The same documentary traceability we apply in maritime classification, now available for your plant.\",\n        \"ic.sup.title\": \"Supplies — Innovation, Sales & Replenishment\",\n        \"ic.sup1.title\": \"1. Ecological Fire Suppression Solutions — Cutting-Edge Technology\",\n        \"ic.sup1.item1.title\": \"Condensed Aerosols — The Most Advanced Technology\",\n        \"ic.sup1.item1.text\": \"Supply and installation of the most advanced and environmentally friendly fire suppression technology on the market. These compact systems extinguish fire at a molecular level without depleting the oxygen in the room, without damaging sensitive electronics and without any impact on the ozone layer. Ideal for server rooms, high-voltage electrical panels and transformer centres. No civil works required — installation in a single day.\",\n        \"ic.sup2.title\": \"2. Wireless Detection Systems\",\n        \"ic.sup2.item1.title\": \"Cable-free Detection — No Civil Works\",\n        \"ic.sup2.item1.text\": \"We supply and install the latest generation of wireless fire detection systems. The perfect solution for industrial warehouses, listed historic buildings or commercial premises that need to update their safety quickly. Installation times are cut in half compared to wired systems, with no need for complex civil works or wall routing.\",\n        \"ic.sup3.title\": \"3. Conventional & Portable Equipment\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item1.title\": \"High-Efficacy Extinguishers — Adapted to Your Fire Load\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item1.text\": \"Sale and replenishment of high-efficacy extinguishers (ABC Powder, CO₂, Water and Foam) adapted to the specific fire load of your business and the type of materials present in each zone. We carry out a fire load study and determine the optimal extinguishing agent for each area of your installation.\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item2.title\": \"Safety Signage & Portable Detection\",\n        \"ic.sup3.item2.text\": \"Complete complementary equipment: photoluminescent evacuation and fire-fighting signage, fire blankets for industrial kitchens, portable gas and CO detectors for maintenance personnel, and respiratory protection equipment for confined spaces.\"\n    }\n};\n\n\n;\n    // Wrapped in an IIFE to avoid polluting the global scope\n    ;\n    (function